Kwiyongera cyane kw'ubwandu bw'indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) muri EU/European Economic Area no mu Bwongereza hagati ya 1 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abandura indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) ugereranyije ugaragaza ihinduka nk'iryo mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, ibyo bikaba byemeza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gikomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu byose nubwo kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye.
Dukurikije ubunararibonye bw'Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bigomba kwitegura kwiyongera kw'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, habonetse icyorezo cya Pneumonia kitaramenyekana icyayiteye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe gukumira no gukumira indwara cyemeje ko icyorezo ari coronavirus nshya ubu izwi nka SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yiswe indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, abagera kuri 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bworoheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bufite cyangwa budafite icyorezo cya pinyabure, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu 14 ku ijana, COVID-19 itera indwara ikomeye cyane igasaba kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe abasigaye 6 ku ijana bagerwaho n'uburwayi bukomeye bukeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Urupfu rw'abarwayi bari mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni hafi 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twarebye uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwagiye buhinduka muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'u Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza (Ubwongereza), maze tugereranya uko byagenze mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'iy'u Butaliyani kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira, kandi ubukana bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ubu buhuje n'icyo gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu igazeti ya Eurosurveillance 2020 yo ku ya 5 Werurwe, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko ari bo bantu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi hakurikijwe ibisobanuro by'ubwandu byatanzwe na OMS.
Mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye, batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bari bavuye i Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bari bamaze kugaragara muri buri gihugu cya 30 cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza uyu munsi, havuzwe abantu 39,768 banduye ndetse n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, muri bo 17 750 banduye ndetse n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye mu Butaliyani honyine.
Gushyiraho umubare n'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19
Mu Kigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzirinda (CEPCM), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi, yavuye gusa ku makuru yemewe nk'inzego z'ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'akarere ndetse na OMS, ihererekanywa buri munsi saa munani z'ijoro.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima iterambere rya COVID-19 mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/umuryango w'ibihugu by'iburayi n'u Bwongereza, no kugereranya n'ubunararibonye bw'Ubutaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo gupima ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19, twabaze imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14, dufata mu mutwe uko COVID-19 yagiye igenda muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twagereranyije kandi umubare w'abanduye muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'amanywa n'ubumenyi bwatanzwe n'u Butaliyani kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Uko COVID-19 yagenze mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Iterambere ry'ubwiyongere bw'iminsi 14 y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu buryo busanzwe bwagiye buhura n'ibyabaye mu ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umuryango w'Ibihugu by'Ibihugu by'Iburengerazuba n'Ubwongereza, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku wa 21 Gashyantare, buza kwiyongera cyane ahagana ku wa 28 Gashyantare 2020 (amakuru y'inyongera).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'abanduye muri Italiya, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byagize ukwiyongera nk'uko mu mibare yose y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 (amakuru y'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'ibyavuye mu Butaliyani kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani z'amanywa, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'umuryango w'ibihugu by'iburayi n'iburasirazuba (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza byari bimaze gutanga raporo y'umubare w'abanduye uhuza n'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu gusa cyangwa munsi y'aho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abandura COVID-19 wiyongera cyane mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umuryango w'Ibihugu by'Iburengerazuba n'u Bwongereza.
Uko imibare y'abandura COVID-19 igenda yiyongera bigaragaza ko icyorezo kigenda gihinduka mu buryo buhuje mu bihugu byose.
Ibi kandi n'ubwo ibihugu bitandukanye biri mu byiciro bitandukanye kandi hari itandukaniro mu bisubizo bitangwa n'inzego z'ubuzima rusange, hari n'itandukaniro mu bisobanuro by'abanduye ndetse n'itandukaniro mu mabwiriza yo gutoranya abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo COVID-19 yemezwe, harimo no gupimwa mu gihe cy'ibizamini.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twugarijwe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani bavuze ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'amavuriro y'abarwayi bakomeye muri utwo turere byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwayo.
Amakuru ajyanye no kwakira abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro no/cyangwa mu byumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye ubu araboneka mu bihugu bya EU/EEA ku kigero cya 6% gusa na 1% by'abarwayi, (amakuru ataratanzwe).
Ariko, hakenewe gukusanya gahunda yo kongerera amakuru y'ubugenzuzi agamije ku mubare w'abamaze kwandura n'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 201011 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini ku mubare w'ibitanda biboneka mu nzego z'ubuvuzi bwa hagati n'ubwitonzi mu Burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29.2 ku bantu 100 000 mu Budage kugeza ku bitanda 4.2 muri Portugal.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bifite umutungo munini cyangwa muke ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe n'ibisanzwe ku bantu 100 000 mu 2010).11
Imiterere y'uburyo bwo kwita ku barwayi, hamwe n'ingero z'ibihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza ku mibare y'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro bafite ibyago byo kurenza 90% by'ibitanda by'abaganga bababaye, byatanzwe mu isesengura rya gatandatu ry'igenzura ry'ibyago bya COVID-19 rya CEPCM.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abarwayi bari mu bice bimwe by'ibihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'amavuriro ya ICU bikunze kwakira abaturage bo mu karere runaka, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitanda bya ICU yagombye gutangwa ku rwego rwa 2 rw'ibaruramari ry'akarere (NUTS 2).
Ibyaranze Ubutaliyani n'ibibera mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda vuba mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/umuryango w'ibihugu by'iburayi n'ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba rero kwitegura icyerekezo cy'ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage ndetse n'iyongerekana ry'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye, nk'uko bimeze mu bice by'u Butaliyani byugarijwe n'iki cyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'igenzura ry'ibyago riherutse gukorwa na CEPCM, uburyo bwihuse, bw'iterambere kandi bwuzuye ni ngombwa mu guhagarika ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, kuva ku buryo bwo guhagarika kugeza ku buryo bwo kugabanya, kuko kwiyongera k'umubare w'abandura hakiri kare bishobora gutuma haba igihe gihagije ku bashyiraho amategeko n'ibitaro cyo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no guhindura uko babyifatamo mu buryo bukwiriye, iyo hataba hari icyo bikorwa mbere.
Ishami ry'ubushakashatsi ku byorezo ryashyize ahagaragara uburyo bwo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari igihe gito buri gihugu gishobora kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ryayo no kugabanya igitutu ku nzego z'ubuzima.
Bitabaye ibyo, birashoboka ko sisitemu z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu bya EU/EEA zizagira umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na SARS-CoV-2, kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3000 no kwandura abantu barenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa no ku isi hose, bituma habaho ibyago by'abantu.
Kimwe na SARS-CoV, yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi barwara SARS mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura binyuze mu ducurama kandi igatera ibimenyetso nk'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite ubukana buciriritse kandi ntiyica cyane nka SARS, ariko irandura cyane, kandi igera ku bantu bakuru kurusha urubyiruko, kandi igera ku bagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza ku kwiyongera k'ibitabo kuri iyi ndwara iri kuvuka, iyi nyandiko yihatira gutanga isuzuma rikwiye kandi rihuje n'igihe kuri iki kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi kirimo kwiyongera.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze byerekeye indwara z'ibyorezo, izifata, virusi, gusuzuma, kuvura, kwemeza indwara n'uburyo bwo kuyirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikiri mu bisubizo, twizeye ko ubu bushakashatsi buzatuma abantu barushaho gusobanukirwa neza indwara ikomeye kandi bakayirwanya.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wo ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wagize ingaruka ku Bashinwa, kuko bagombaga kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cy'icyumweru cyose cy'amavuko ndetse no mu yindi minsi myinshi kubera ikwirakwira ry'indwara nshya y'ubwandu.
Iyi virusi imeze neza nka coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka (SARS) mu mwaka wa 2003; ni yo mpamvu yashyizwe ku rutonde rwa SARS-CoV-2 n'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020, ndetse n'indwara ifitanye isano na yo yitwa coronavirus disease 19 (COVID-19).
Icyorezo cyatangiriye i Wuhan, cyihuse gikwira mu Bushinwa bwose, mbere yo gukwirakwira mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yari imaze gutuma abantu barenga 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abasaga 40.000 bakaba baramaze kujya mu bitaro, naho abasaga 3.000 bakaba barapfuye.
OMS ivuga ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi wa mbere w'abaturage, ushobora kuba uteje akaga kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hamaze gutangwa ibitabo bisaga 200 ku bijyanye na COVID-19, cyane cyane mu bijyanye na virusi, indwara z'ibyorezo, indwara ziterwa n'imiterere y'umubiri, gusuzuma no kuvura, kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku wa 7 Mutarama 2020 yerekanaga uko virusi yagendaga ikurikirana, yavuye ku barwayi benshi.
Iyi nyigo igerageza gusesengura intambwe y'ubushakashatsi kuri iki kibazo gishya gikomeje kwiyongera.
Mu gihe cya vuba, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara ya coronavirus, indwara yo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyabaye mu mwaka wa 2012).
Tuzasuzuma kandi ibyo twamaze kumenya ku bijyanye no kwirinda no kumenya uko indwara ishobora kuzabaho, kandi tuzasuzuma ibibazo bimwe na bimwe bikiriho ariko byihutirwa.
Koronavirusi zisanzwe zifatwa nk'indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi zitagira icyo zitwara abantu, zikagaragaza ko ziterwa n'uburwayi bw'ibicurane hafi ya 15%.
Ariko muri iki kinyejana, twabonye koronavirusi ebyiri ziteye indwara nyinshi ku bantu, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye habaho icyorezo cyatangiye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, mbere yo gukwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi bifite ubwandu bwinshi n'ubwandu bwinshi.
COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya coronavirus mu mateka y'iki gihe.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho ya 1.1, icyorezo cya Pneumonia cy'inkomoko itaramenyekana cyavuzwe bwa mbere muri Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kuri Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'Ubushinwa.
Hashize iminsi irindwi, icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiye kugaragara.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wapfuye yabonetse mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyari cyarakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu by'ibituranyi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, byatangajwe ko abaganga banduye, bivuga ko bishobora kuba byarakwirakwijwe hagati y'abantu.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan washyizwe mu kato, imodoka zose za leta zihagarikwa.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku ndwara bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 bemejwe ko banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bagaragaye ko bari mu isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, rifatwa nk'aho ari ho hatangiriye ubwandu buturutse ku nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yandikwaga, iyi ndwara yari imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 hirya no hino ku isi (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo.2).2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka vuba, umubare n'uburemere by'icyorezo biracyari kugenwa.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bigo byinshi ku barwayi 8,866, barimo 4,021 bemeje ko banduye COVID-19, bwagaragaje uko iki cyorezo cyagenze (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Ul-Bi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yanduriraga abantu b'imyaka yose, ariko cyane cyane mu kigero cy'imyaka 30-65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47,7%) cy'abanduye bari bafite imyaka iri hejuru ya 50, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20, kandi 14 gusa bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yanduzaga abagabo cyane (0,31/100.000) kurusha abagore (0,27/100.000).
COVID-19 yari ikwirakwira mu ngo, cyane cyane mu ntara ya Hubei no mu nkengero zayo.
