Icyakora, guterwa umuti wa remdesivir mu mitsi, ni kimwe mu bintu byafasha umuntu ufite COVID-19 muri Amerika.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya urwanya virusi watangiranye n'ikigo cya Gilead mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi za Ebola na Marburg.
Nyuma yaho, remdesivir yagaragaje ko ishobora kubuza izindi virusi zifite umugozi umwe wa RNA, harimo MERS na SARS.
Nyuma y'ibi byatangajwe, Gilead yahaye Ubushinwa uwo muti kugira ngo ibone uko ikora ibizamini ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi hari icyizere cyinshi cy'uko bizagenda neza.
Byongeye kandi baricitinib, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir hamwe na ribavirin byashyizwe ahagaragara nk'uburyo bushobora kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero.
Ibiribwa birimo: diarrhoea, gusinda, kuruka, kwangirika kw'umura n'ibindi byorezo bishobora kubaho nyuma yo gufatwa na lopinavir/ritonavir.
Imikorere y'izo miti hamwe n'izindi miti zikoreshwa mu barwayi igomba kugenzurwa neza.
Plasma y'abarwayi bakize n'igikorwa cy'umubiri
Gukuza amaraso ku barwayi bakize indwara zandura kugira ngo bavurwe abandi barwayi bafite iyo ndwara cyangwa kurinda abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza iyo ndwara ni umugenzo wa kera.
Ni ukubera ko abarwayi bakize akenshi baba bafite ibice by'umubiri by'umubiri bihanze ubwandu.
Abarwayi ni immunoglobuline (Ig) ikorwa na linfocyte B mu kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'imiti n'ibindi binyabuzima by'amahanga; bamenya molekile zidasanzwe mu ndwara ziterwa n'imiti kandi bakazica.
Plasma yakuwe mu maraso y'itsinda ry'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze ishyirwa mu miti ku barwayi 10 barwaye cyane.
Ibimenyetso byabo byagiye birushaho kuba byiza mu masaha 24, bifatanyije no kugabanuka kw'uburwayi, kugabanuka kw'umuriro wa virusi no kuzamuka kw'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Ariko kandi, hakenewe igenzura no gusobanura neza uburyo bwo gukoresha ubu buryo ku rugero rwagutse kugeza igihe hazaba hatangiye gukorwa uburyo bwihariye bwo kubukoresha.
Byongeye kandi, bitewe n'ingaruka zo kuvura, hari ingaruka zimwe na zimwe ziterwa na plasma zikwiye gusuzumwa neza.
