TCM imaze imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi ikoreshwa mu Bushinwa mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye.
Ariko ingaruka zayo ahanini zishingiye ku guhuza ibice byinshi mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'igikorwa cyo gupima, gishingiye ku bitekerezo bya TCM.
Ibyinshi mu bice bifite imbaraga biracyari bike cyangwa nta na kimwe bizwi kuko bigoye kubikuramo no kubisuzuma, cyangwa kumenya imikoranire yabyo myiza.
Muri iki gihe, kubera ko nta muti wihariye ushobora kuvura COVID-19, TCM ni imwe mu miti y'ibanze ikoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa bito cyangwa bafite indwara ikomeye.
Urugero, Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen byagaragaye ko ari byo bikora neza mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibipimo byiza byo gukira COVID-19 byabonetse mu ntara z'Ubushinwa zakoresheje TCM ku barwayi 87% harimo intara ya Gansu (63,7%), akarere ka Ningxia (50%) na Hunan (50%), naho intara ya Hubei, yakoresheje TCM ku barwayi 30% gusa ba COVID-19, ifite igipimo cyo hasi cyo gukira (13%).
