Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang n'abo bafatanyije basohoye ubushakashatsi bugereranya uburyo bwo kuvura hakoreshejwe imiti y'iburengerazuba gusa (MO) n'uburyo bwo kuvura hakoreshejwe MO n'imiti y'ubwoko butandukanye (TBC).
