Igitangaje kurushaho, ni uko igipimo cyo kwiyongera k'ibimenyetso (kuva ku byoroheje kugeza ku bikomeye) cyari hasi cyane mu itsinda rya MO+MTC kurusha mu itsinda rya MO gusa (7,4% kuri 46,2%); kimwe n'uko urupfu rwari hasi mu itsinda rya MO+MTC kurusha mu itsinda rya MO gusa (8,8% kuri 39%).
Nyamara, ubuziranenge n'ubwirinzi bwa TCM biracyari mu bigeragezo by'ubuziranenge byakozwe ku rwego runini kurushaho no mu bigo byinshi.
Byari kuba byiza kandi gusobanura uburyo bw'ibikorwa no gusobanura neza ibice by'ubuvuzi bwa TCM cyangwa se guhuza, niba bishoboka.
