Inkomoko ya zoonotic ya coronavirus z'abantu
Ibyago byo kwandura indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS) n'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) byahinduye imiterere, bigaragaza ko ubwandu bwa HCoV bushobora kuba bubi cyane kandi bukagira ingaruka mbi.
HCoV nyinshi zituruka ku ducurama, aho zitandura.
Imibare y'ibimenyetso by'uko virusi ya HCoV ishobora guhitana abantu benshi cyane, igaragaza ko hari abantu benshi bashobora guhitana abantu benshi cyane.
Kumenya inyamaswa zitera indwara bigira ingaruka ku buryo butaziguye mu gukumira indwara mu bantu.
Gusuzuma imikorere ya CoV mu nyamaswa bishobora no gutuma abantu barushaho gusobanukirwa CoV.
Ukurikije itandukaniro ry'ibinyabuzima, CoVs zashyizwe mu miryango ine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV).
Ibimenyetso by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byagaragaje ko udukoko n'imbeba ari byo bikurura alpha-CoVs nyinshi na beta-CoVs, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zikurura cyane gamma-CoVs na delta-CoVs.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana abantu barindwi bafite virusi ya CoV (HCoV).
Muri byo, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni alpha-CoV.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
Gukurikirana inkomoko ya HCoV mu nyamaswa zitandura bitanga urufatiro rwo gusobanukirwa amateka y'ibanze, imbaraga zituma habaho ubwandu n'ibintu bibangamira uko ubwoko bw'imiti bwambuka.
Nanone kandi, ishobora kuyobora cyangwa gufasha mu gushakisha aho SARS-CoV-2 iherereye, ikwirakwira hagati yayo n'aho ikwirakwira, bigira ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira ubwandu bw'igihe kizaza.
CoV z'amatungo zamenyekanye kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30.
Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, hamaze kuvumburwa virusi zirindwi za HCoV.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E bwavumbuwe mu buryo bwo guhumeka mu barwayi bafite ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru mu 1966, nyuma buza gukurira mu miterere y'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu bihaha ya WI-38.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya ruswa isanzwe, harimo umutwe, kwiyuha akuya, kumva batameze neza no kuribwa mu muhogo, hamwe n'umuriro n'igicuri mu 10 kugeza kuri 20% by'abarwayi.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi biboneka ku isi hose kandi bisa n'aho byandurira cyane cyane mu bihe by'imbeho mu bihugu bifite ikirere gishyushye.
