Nubwo ijambo  icyorezo  ryerekeza gusa ku burebure bw'icyorezo, ntabwo ari ku kaga k'ubwandu bwihariye, OMS yagaragaje ko hakenewe guhatira leta kugira icyo zikora:
 Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze ko ibihugu bigomba gupima, gupima, kuvura, gutandukanya, gushakisha no guhuza abaturage babyo mu gisubizo.
 Dufite impungenge zikomeye, atari ku mibare iteye ubwoba y'ikwirakwira n'uburemere bwayo gusa, ahubwo no ku mibare iteye ubwoba y'ubushomeri. 
Dr Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo  kitigeze kibaho .
Mu magambo yashyizwe ahagaragara na CNN muri Gashyantare, yavuze ko uretse ibicurane, nta bindi byorezo by'ubuhumekero byigeze biboneka kuva byatangira kugeza ubwo bikomeje gukwirakwira ku isi hose.
Ghebreyesus na we yavuze ko  tutigeze tubona icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus. 
Yongeyeho ati:  kandi ntitwabonye  icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe. 
