Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20 ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya Coronavirus (COVID-19) cyatangiye kuva mu mwaka wa 2019, cyatewe na Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Icyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangajwe ko ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu ku isi hose ku ya 30 Mutarama 2020 ndetse cyemezwa ko ari icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bikaba byarabahitanye bagera ku 97,000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
Igiciro cy'abapfa kigereranywa ko ari 4% mu Bushinwa, mu gihe mu bindi bice by'isi gituruka kuri 13.04% muri Algeria kugeza kuri 0.08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
