Umubare w'abahitanywe na COVID-19 ushobora kuba uri hejuru cyane, kuko ushobora kuba utari ukubiyemo abantu bapfuye batageragejwe - urugero nko mu ngo, mu ngo z'abageze mu za bukuru n'ibindi.
Amakuru y'igice yo mu Butaliyani agaragaza ko imibare y'abapfuye cyane muri iki cyorezo iri hejuru inshuro 4-5 y'ibarura ry'abishwe na COVID.
Umuvugizi w'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye  Tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye] utangwaho amakuru atari yo , amagambo yemejwe n'amakuru y'ibyavuzwe ku buryo butari bwo muri Amerika. Uko gutangwaho amakuru atari yo akenshi biba mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'indwara z'ibyorezo, nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube H1N1 cyo mu mwaka wa 2009. Urupfu rwa mbere rwemejwe rwabereye i Wuhan ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020.
Umuntu wa mbere wapfuye hanze y'Ubushinwa yabonetse ku ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho uwa mbere wapfuye hanze ya Aziya yabonetse mu Bufaransa ku ya 14 Gashyantare.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'Ubushinwa, abantu barenga 12 bapfuye muri Iran, Koreya y'Epfo no mu Butaliyani.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu n'uturere birenga 40 byari byatangaje ko hari abantu bapfuye, ku migabane yose uretse Antarctica. Ibimenyetso bitandukanye bikoreshwa mu gupima umubare w'abapfa.
Iyi mibare itandukanye bitewe n'akarere ndetse n'igihe, kandi igira ingaruka ku mubare w'ibipimo, ireme ry'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe kimaze kuva icyorezo cyatangira, hamwe n'ibintu by'abaturage birimo imyaka, igitsina, cyane cyane ubuzima.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ibaruramari rya kaminuza ya Johns-Hopkins, umubare w'abapfuye ku isi ni 6,0% (97 039/1 617 204) ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare w'abapfuye utandukanye bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'ubwandu n'urupfu yagabanutse kuva kuri 17,3% (ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso hagati ya 1 na 10 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0,7% (ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso nyuma ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ibindi bimenyetso ni igipimo cy'urupfu (igereranyo y'urupfu), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu basanganywe indwara bapfa, n'igereranyo y'ubwandu (igereranyo y'ubwandu), kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye (bafashwe cyangwa batarafashwe) bapfa bazize indwara.
Izi mibare ntabwo zifite igihe gihagije kandi zikurikirana abaturage runaka bafite ubwandu ku iherezo ry'indwara.
Abahanga mu bya siyansi benshi bagerageje kubara imibare y'abantu runaka.
Ikigo cya Oxford Center for Evidence-Based Medicine gitekereza ko ubwandu bw'icyorezo muri rusange buri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Igiciro cyo hejuru muri iki cyiciro gihuza n'ibyavuye mu igerageza rya mbere rya COVID-19 mu Budage, n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bipimo by'imibare by'ingaruka z'igerageza ku bipimo by'ubwandu.
OMS ivuga ko icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Ikiringo cyo hejuru n'igihe cy'icyorezo ntibiramenyekana kandi bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya Pennsylvania State yavuze ko:  Iyo ntagenzurwa, ubusanzwe indwara zandura zigenda zikomera hanyuma zigatangira gukendera igihe indwara itangiye kubura abarwayi.
Ariko muri iki gihe, gukora igishushanyo mbonera cy'igihe ibyo bizabera biragoye cyane.
Umujyanama mukuru w'ubuvuzi muri guverinoma y'Ubushinwa Zhong Nanshan yavuze ko  bishobora kurangira muri Kamena  niba ibihugu byose byashoboye gushyira hamwe bikurikiza inama za OMS ku ngamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu ishuri ry'i Londres ryigisha iby'isuku n'ubuvuzi bwo mu karere k'ibiyaga bigari yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2  izakomeza gukwirakwira, ishobora kumara umwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri .
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson muri Imperial College, bwagaragaje ko abantu bagomba kwirinda kujya kure y'abandi ndetse n'ibindi bikorwa by'ubutabazi kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze kuboneka (hashobora kuba hashize amezi 18 cyangwa arenga).
William Schaffner wo muri kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati: "Ntekereza ko bishoboka ko iyi coronavirus, kuko yandura cyane, itazashiraho burundu, kandi ko ishobora guhinduka indwara y'ibihe by'umwaka, ishobora kugaruka buri mwaka".
Uburemere bw'iki cyorezo kiza kugaruka buzaterwa n'ubwirinzi bw'abantu benshi ndetse n'ubw'imiterere y'iyi virusi.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 hari igihe biba bidasanzwe, kandi abantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara cyane ni umuriro (88%) n'inkorora (68%).
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe birimo umunaniro, gutakaza umwuka (mucosities), kubura impumuro, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu myuniko no mu ngingo, kuribwa mu muhogo, umutwe, gutinya, kuruka, kurwara umutima, gucibwamwo, cyangwa cyanoze. OMS ivuga ko hafi umuntu umwe kuri batandatu arwaye cyane kandi afite ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika (CDC) cyerekana ibimenyetso by'ubutabazi nko guhumeka nabi, kubabara cyangwa guturika kw'igituza bidashira, urujijo rutunguranye, kubyuka bigoye, n'uruhu cyangwa iminwa y'ubururu; kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihuse n'abaganga mu gihe ibimenyetso biriho.
Bamwe mu bantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso, nta bimenyetso byo mu buvuzi bafite ariko bagasanga ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi batanze inama ko abantu bagiranye imishyikirano ya bugufi n'abantu banduye bagombye gukurikiranwa cyane no gusuzumwa kugira ngo hatagira ubwandu.
Ibipimo by'Abashinwa by'umubare w'abatabyigaragazaho ibimenyetso bituruka kuri bake kugera kuri 44%.
Igihe gisanzwe cyo guhumeka (igihe kiri hagati yo kwandura no kugaragaza ibimenyetso) kiri hagati y'umunsi umwe n'iminsi 14, ariko akenshi ni iminsi itanu.
Hari amakuru menshi ku buryo iyi ndwara ikwirakwira.
Byitezwe ko iyi ndwara yandurira cyane cyane mu buryo bwo guhanahana imibonano ya bugufi no mu guturika kw'amazi ku buryo bworoshye biturutse ku guhohotera, kwitsamura cyangwa kuvuga; ubwo buryo bwo guhanahana imibonano ya bugufi bugereranywa n'umurambararo wa metero 1 kugeza kuri 2 (metero 3 kugeza kuri 6).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko iyo umuntu akoroye nta cyo arinze, ashobora guterera amazi mu kirere ari hagati ya metero 4,5 na metero 8.2.
Bamwe bavuze ko virusi ishobora no gukwirakwira binyuze mu dutonyanga duto tuva mu mwuka mu gihe kirekire, dushobora guturuka mu kanwa mu gihe umuntu avuga.
Ibibyimba bishobora kugwa mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abandi bantu bari hafi cyangwa se bikajya mu bihaha.
Bimwe mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi nk'imiti yo gutera no guhagarika umutima (CPR) bishobora gutuma imyanda yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero isohoka ikajya mu mwuka, bityo igakwirakwira mu kirere.
Iyo ndwara ishobora kandi kwandura iyo umuntu akoze ku kintu cyanduye, urugero nk'uruhu, mbere yo gukora ku maso, mu mazuru cyangwa mu kanwa.
Niba hari abatinya ko ishobora kwandurira mu byo kurya, iki kibazo gifatwa nk'ikidashobora gukemuka.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yanze ko SARS-CoV-2 yandura binyuze mu kanwa mu gihe cy'iminsi itatu ya mbere ibimenyetso byatangiye, ariko bishobora gukwirakwira mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira no mu gihe cy'indwara y'icyorezo.
Abantu bapimwe neza barwaye kugeza ku minsi itatu mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragaza ko kwanduza bishoboka mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bikomeye bitangira kugaragara.
Hari raporo nke z'abandura batagira ibimenyetso byemejwe na laboratoire, ariko hari ibihugu byabonye ko abantu batagira ibimenyetso byandura mu gihe cy'ubushakashatsi.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo tutaramenya neza uburyo indwara yandura, umuntu umwe ashobora kwanduza abandi babiri cyangwa batatu.
