Ubu leta nyinshi zisaba cyangwa zisaba abantu kwirinda mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Umubare munini w'abantu bashobora guhurira hamwe wahanuwe na leta ya Amerika n'inzego z'ubuzima wahise ugabanuka uva ku bantu 250 (nta muntu n'umwe uzwi ufite COVID-19 muri ako karere) ugera ku bantu 50, nyuma haje abantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwabujije guteranira hamwe mu ruhame by'abantu barenga babiri. Abantu bakuru n'abafite ibibazo by'ubuzima nk'igisukari, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso cyangwa uburwayi bw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye n'izindi ndwara. CDC yabasabye kuguma mu rugo uko bishoboka kose mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima batangiye gusimbuza ijambo "gukomeza gutandukanya abantu" na "gukomeza gutandukanya abantu", kugira ngo basobanure intego yo kugabanya imibonano mpuzabitsina binyuze mu gukomeza imishyikirano, haba mu buryo busanzwe cyangwa mu buryo bwo kwirinda.
Gukoresha ijambo  gutandukanya abantu  byumvikanisha ko abantu bagomba kwigunga burundu, aho gushishikariza abantu gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi mu bundi buryo. Abayobozi bamwe batanze amabwiriza ajyanye n'ubuzima bw'imyororokere mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Muri byo harimo inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu mubana gusa, udafite virusi cyangwa udagaragaza ibimenyetso.
Abantu basanganywe COVID-19 n'abakekwaho kuyandura, basabwe kuguma mu ngo zabo.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza arambuye yo kwitandukanya neza n'abandi, kandi leta nyinshi zashyizeho cyangwa zashishikariza abantu bose baba mu turere twugarijwe n'iyo ndwara kwitandukanya n'abandi.
Amabwiriza yo kwigumira mu kato ku giti cyabo akomeye cyane yatanzwe ku bantu bari mu matsinda y'abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura.
Abantu bagaragarijwe umurwayi wa COVID-19 n'abaherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa mu karere kagize ubwandu bukabije basabwe kwicungira ukwabo mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bashoboraga kuba baraherukaga kugaragara.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura icyorezo ni ukugihagarika cyangwa kugihashya, no kugihosha.
Gukumira indwara byatangiye mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, bigamije gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu banduye, no gushyiraho ubundi buryo bwo kugenzura indwara no gukingira kugira ngo birinde ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu baturage.
Iyo nta bushobozi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara buhari, imbaraga zijya mu cyiciro cyo kugabanya: ingamba zifatwa zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara no kugabanya ingaruka zayo ku rwego rw'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Ingamba zo gukumira no kugabanya ingaruka z'ibi byago zishobora gufatwa icyarimwe.
Gukumira birasaba ingamba zikomeye cyane zo kugabanya icyorezo mu kugabanya umubare w'ubwandu ku kigero kiri munsi ya 1. Kimwe mu byo umuntu akora mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'indwara zandura ni ukugerageza kugabanya ubukana bw'icyorezo: ibyo ni byo byitwa gutunganya icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kurengera serivisi z'ubuzima no kugura igihe cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Mu bikorwa bitari ibiyobyabwenge bishobora kurwanya iki cyorezo harimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kwirinda gukaraba intoki, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwigunga; ingamba za Leta zo kwirinda abantu, nko gufunga amashuri n'ibigo by'idini; imbaraga za Leta zo gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibyo bikorwa; hamwe n'ibikorwa byo kubungabunga ibidukikije, nko gusukura. Ingamba zikomeye zo kugabanya iki cyorezo zafatiwe mu Bushinwa ubwo byagaragaye ko ari icyorezo, nko gushyira imijyi yose mu kato no kubuza ingendo.
Ibindi bihugu na byo byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho ibipimo by'abantu benshi no gushyira abantu mu kato, kandi itanga imiburo ku bantu banduye iyo bagiye.
Singapuru yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye bari biyemeje kwigenga, kandi yishyura amande menshi ku batayemeye.
Tayiwani yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa kandi itegeka ko hafatwa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ibigereranyo byakozwe mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika bigaragaza ko guhangana (kugabanya ariko kudakuraho ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kucyirinda (guhindura icyorezo) biri mu bibazo bikomeye.
Amategeko yo kugabanya ubukana bw'indwara ashobora kugabanya ibura ry'ubuvuzi ku bice bibiri bya gatatu, n'urupfu rugatumbagira, ariko ntashobora gukumira ibihumbi amagana by'abapfa, kandi imibereho y'abavuzi irarembye.
Gukuraho virusi bishobora guhabwa umwanya w'ibanze, ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze kuboneka, niba ari rwo ruza mbere), kuko bitabaye ibyo, ikwirakwira rizahita risubira inyuma mu gihe ingamba zo kugabanya virusi zigiye kugabanuka.
Gufata ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhashya icyorezo bifite ikiguzi mu rwego rw'imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta miti yemewe ya COVID-19 ikoreshwa mu kurwanya virusi, ariko hari ibikorwa byo kuyikoresha birimo gukorwa, harimo no kugerageza imiti ikoreshwa.
Kunywa imiti ya ruswa cyangwa inzoga hamwe no kuruhuka bishobora gufasha mu kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Ukurikije ubukana bw'iki cyorezo, imiti yo gufata umwuka, guterwa amaraso mu mitsi no gufashwa guhumeka bishobora gukenerwa.
Gukoresha imiti ya Steroide bishobora gutuma ingaruka zirushaho kuba mbi.
Imyinshi mu miti yemewe mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS yavuze ko imiti imwe n'imwe ikoreshwa mu buvuzi bw'ibanze ishobora koroshya ibimenyetso bya SARS-CoV-19.
Kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ubuvuzi n'ibikenewe n'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bivugwa na OMS nk'ingamba z'ibanze zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere by'umuryango w'abibumbye byita ku buzima mu Burayi byashyize ahagaragara amabwiriza agenga ibitaro n'inzego z'ubuvuzi by'ibanze ku bijyanye no kongera gukoresha umutungo mu byiciro bitandukanye, harimo gushyira ibikoresho bya laboratwari mu gupima COVID-19, guhagarika ibikorwa bitari iby'ubutabazi mu gihe bishoboka, gutandukanya no gushyira mu kato abarwayi bagaragaye ko banduye COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bw'abashinzwe kwita ku barwayi bakomeye binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibyinyo byo guhumeka n'ibiro bihari.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku byerekeye aho umuntu wa mbere (witwa umurwayi wa zeru) yakomotse.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko yanduye coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba yongeye kugaragara ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu kwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wiyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ubusanzwe bifitanye isano n'isoko rya Huanan ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja, ryakundaga no gucuruza inyamaswa nzima. Hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ishobora kuba yaturutse kuri imwe muri izo nyamaswa; mu yandi magambo, ishobora kuba yarakomotse ku nyamaswa. Ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, habonetse icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane bitamenyekana, cyitabwaho na Dr Zhang Jixian mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei, maze kuri uyu wa 27 Ukuboza, CDC yo mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Jianghan imenyesha ko iki cyorezo cyatewe n'iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ko hari virusi ya corona isa na SARS.
Abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang, bakatiwe na polisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha, naho undi witwa Ai Fen, yakatiwe n'abayobozi be kubera ko yatanze amakuru.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umurenge wa Wuhan nyuma yaho yasohoye itangazo ku mugaragaro ku ya 31 Ukuboza, kandi imenyesha OMS.
Hari abantu benshi babonetse bafite indwara ya Pneumonia itaramenyekana, babimenyesheje inzego z'ubuzima za Wuhan kugira ngo batangize iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati muri Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa, ibi bikaba byatewe n'ubwiyongere bw'abimukira mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa ndetse n'uko Wuhan ari ikigo cy'ingendo ndetse n'ahantu hakomeye hakorerwamo ingendo za gari ya moshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje abantu bashya bagera kuri 140 mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzhen.
Amakuru y'ibanze ya nyuma agaragaza ko abantu 6 174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatsinze Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani mu kugaragaza umubare munini w'abanduye ku isi. Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abanduye barenga miliyoni 1.61 batangajwe ku isi hose; abantu barenga 97.000 barapfuye, abandi barenga 364.000 barakira.
Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 byagize nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije Uburayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije ingendo no gushyiraho igenzura ku mipaka.
Ibisubizo mu gihugu byaranzwe n'ingamba zo gukumira, nko gushyira abantu mu kato (byitwa kandi kuguma mu rugo, gufungura cyangwa gufunga) no gushyiraho amasaha yo gutaha. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa 90% by'abaturage, bari mu gukumira muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari muri Filipine, abagera kuri miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo na miliyari 1,3 mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari bafite uburyo runaka bwo gufungirwa, umubare wariyongereye ugera kuri miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri  hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umurwayi wa mbere wa COVID-19 wabonetse ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo itaremezwa igaragaza ko uwa mbere wabonetse ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jixian yabonye icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, maze abimenyesha CDC y'i Wuhan Jianghan ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere by'imiterere y'ibimenyetso by'abarwayi byakozwe ku wa 27 Ukuboza 2019 byagaragaje ko hari virusi ya SARS.
Itangazo ry'abaturage ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umurenge wa Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
LOMS yamenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Abaganga bo muri Wuhan bahawe umuburo kubera ko bakwirakwije ibihuha by'icyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta gihamya igaragara y'uko umuntu ashobora kwandura undi muntu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye, nyuma y'aho buvugwa n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping nk'intambara y'abaturage yo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Mu byiswe  kwigunga gukomeye kurusha ibindi mu mateka y'abantu , ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe ko hateganyijwe gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo zituruka i Wuhan, zikwirakwizwa mu mijyi 15 yo mu mujyi wa Hubei, zigera kuri miliyoni 57 z'abantu bose hamwe.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byarabujijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki 25 Mutarama) byasubitswe mu duce twinshi.
Abayobozi batangaje kandi ko bagiye kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, Huoshenshan, byamaze iminsi 10.
Nyuma y'aho, hubatswe ikindi bitaro, ari cyo Leishenshan, kugira ngo kijye gifasha abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 i Wuhan, nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro na sitade, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho ingamba nshya zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga imenyekanisha ry'ubuzima ku bantu bakora ingendo no kongera iminsi mikuru y'ibiruhuko.
Kaminuza n'amashuri byo mu gihugu nabyo byarafunzwe.
Akarere ka Hong Kong na Macao katangije ingamba nyinshi cyane cyane ku mashuri na za kaminuza.
Ingamba zo gukora kure zashyizweho mu turere twinshi tw'Ubushinwa.
Imipaka yo gutembera yashyizweho muri Hubei no hanze yaho.
Itemberezwa rya rusange ryahinduwe, kandi amazu ndangamurage yo mu Bushinwa arafunze by'agateganyo.
Gucunga ingendo z'abaturage byashyizwe mu bikorwa mu mijyi myinshi, kandi byemejwe ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bari bafite uburyo runaka bwo guhagarika ingendo. Nyuma y'uko icyorezo cyadutse ku isi hose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi ivanwa mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo kwigunga ku bantu bose bakora ingendo mpuzamahanga binjira mu mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa, hari umuntu umwe gusa wanduye mu gihugu mu minsi itanu ishize, binyuze ku muntu wari uvuye i Istanbul agarutse i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe Li Keqiang yavuze ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwanduye mu gihugu cyahagaritswe, kandi ko icyorezo cyahagaritswe mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingamba zo gutembera zarorohejwe muri Hubei, usibye Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo gufunga. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura mu gihugu bizasiba guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko ntivuga igihe iyo gahunda izarangirira.
Abantu bashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula z'u Bushinwa.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije inganda no mu nganda gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga gahunda zo gukangurira inganda amafaranga. Inama y'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kuboroga uzatangira ku isaha ya saa kumi n'imwe z'umugoroba ku ya 4 Mata, uhura n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo guverinoma yo hagati yasabye imiryango guha icyubahiro abantu ku mbuga nkoranyambaga kugira ngo bubahirize itandukanyamibiri no kwirinda kongera kwongera kwanduza COVID-19.
Byemejwe ko COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye muri Koreya y'Epfo ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020 ivuye mu Bushinwa.
Urwego rw'igihugu rw'ubuzima rwatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye wazamutse cyane ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, ahanini bitewe n'ikoraniro ryabereye i Daegu ry'idini rishya ryitwa Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abayoboke ba Shincheonji bari basuye Daegu baturutse i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba ari bo batumye iki cyorezo kivuka.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iri dini, 1,261 cyangwa hafi 13% bavuze ko bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020 ariho hagiye habaho ubwitonzi bukabije.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2.000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, hakurikiraho abantu 3.150 ku ya 29 Gashyantare.
Ibigo bya gisirikare byose byo muri Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu basuzumwe basanga bafite virusi.
Amatariki y'indege na yo yagabanyijwe, bityo ahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda yafashwe nk'iyiganje kandi iteguwe neza kurusha izindi ku isi yo gupima abaturage bakandura virusi, no gushyira mu kato abantu bose banduye, no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima harimo gutanga raporo ku giti cyabo ku bimenyetso by'abashya baturutse mu mahanga bakoresheje porogaramu ya terefone ngendanwa, gupima virusi ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima kugira ngo abantu bagera ku 20.000 bapimwe buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'iy'ibanze mu kurwanya icyorezo, nubwo itashyize mu kato imijyi yose.
Abanyakoreya benshi basinye impapuro zisaba ko Moon ashinjwa uburyo leta itari ifite uburyo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo cyangwa se bagashimira uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yagize umubare muto w'abanduye buri munsi mu byumweru bine.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bazava mu mahanga bazajya bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje, ku itariki ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ubutumire bw'ibihugu 121 byo kuyisaba ubufasha mu gupima virusi.
Irani yatangaje ko abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 19 Gashyantare mu mujyi wa Qom, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi mu by'Ubuvuzi yavuze ko abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'aho kuri uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, siporo n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, ndetse no gufunga kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miriyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'u Rwanda yo kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twugarijwe n'icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Imigambi yo kugabanya ingendo zo mu mijyi itandukanye yatangaje muri Werurwe, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwinshi hagati y'imijyi rwagumyeho mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya wa Norouz.
Ahantu hatagatifu h'Abashia i Qom hagumye hagaragara kugeza ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020. Irani yabaye ikigo cy'ikwirakwira rya virusi nyuma y'Ubushinwa mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare.
Nyuma y'ibyavuzwe ko hashobora kuba hari abantu bagihishe icyorezo cya Iran, ibihugu birenga icumi byari byaravuze ko abarwayi babonetse muri Iran ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, bivuga ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha abarwayi 388 leta ya Irani yari yatangaje kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, mu gihe 23 mu bagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko 290 bavuze ko basuzumwe basanga bafite virusi ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza kurekura byimazeyo abarwanashyaka b'uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira ko batemera amahoro, no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zikwiriye.
L'organisation yavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi mu bigo byugarijwe nk'ibigo by'ifungwa, nabyo bidafite ubuvuzi.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, ari bwo bwa mbere muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba Iran bariho cyangwa bariho, ndetse n'abari muri guverinoma, bishwe n'icyo cyorezo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha, n'undi muntu wapfaga buri minota icumi kubera coronavirus.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi wa OMS, mu gihugu cya Irani hashobora kuba hari abantu benshi banduye kurusha uko byavuzwe inshuro eshanu.
Hari kandi n'ibitekerezo ko ibihano bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bishobora kwangiza ubushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'imari bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ibiro bya Komisiyo y'Ikirenga y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye y'Uburenganzira bwa Muntu byasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu byoroherezwa ibihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Byemejwe ko icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku wa 31 Mutarama, ubwo ba mukerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bagaragazwa ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Abanduye batangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege zijya n'izava mu Bushinwa, ndetse itangaza ko ari mu bihe by'ubukene.
Nyuma yaho, habonetse abantu 16 banduye COVID-19 mu karere ka Lombardie ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo kurwanya icyorezo, harimo no gushyira abantu barenga 50.000 mu kato mu mirenge 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yavuze ko:  Mu bice byibasiwe n'icyorezo, nta muntu uzinjira cyangwa ngo asohoke.
Imirimo y'ubucuruzi n'imikino byamaze guhagarikwa muri utwo turere. Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu, mu gihe mu Butaliyani hapfuye abantu 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya Serie A y'umupira w'amaguru, yagombaga kuba mu nzu z'abakinnyi kugeza mu kwezi kwa kane, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, siporo yose yahagaritswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bihagarara, usibye amaduka manini n'amafashini. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, sosiyete yo mu Butaliyani y'ubuvuzi, ubuvuzi, ubutabazi n'ubuvuzi bukomeye (SIAARTI) yasohoye inama z'imibanire y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye n'amabwiriza yo gutandukanya abantu bashobora gukurikiza.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwatsinze Ubushinwa mu bihugu bifite umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye bazira coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga raporo y'abantu 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'igisirikare zikorerwamo ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128,948 bamaze kwandura, hapfuye 15,887 kandi hari abantu 21,815 bakize; abenshi muri abo bantu bari mu karere ka Lombardie.
Raporo ya CNN yavuze ko guhuza umubare munini w'abageze mu za bukuru mu Butaliyani n'ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bose banduye virusi kugeza ubu bishobora kuba byaratumye habaho umubare munini w'abapfa.
Igisubizo cy'u Bwongereza kuri virusi cyabanje kugaragara nk'ikinyuranyo mu bihugu byibasiwe n'iyo ndwara, kandi kugeza ku itariki ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'u Bwongereza ntiyigeze ishyiraho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutandukanya abantu cyangwa gushyira abantu mu kato.
Ku bw'ibyo, leta yanenzwe kubera ko igaragaza ko itabyitayeho kandi ko itagize icyo ikora mu guhangana n'ibibazo by'abaturage. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko atagomba gukora ingendo zose n'abantu bataba ngombwa, avuga ko abantu bagomba gukorera mu ngo zabo igihe bishoboka, kandi bakirinda ahantu nko mu tubari, mu masoko no mu mazu y'imyidagaduro.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro nka za pub n'amazu y'imikino bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi isezeranya kwishyura kugeza kuri 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi, ku gipimo cya £2,500 ku kwezi, mu rwego rwo kwirinda ubushomeri bushingiye ku nkunga. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda abantu guterana, abuza guteranira hamwe abantu barenga babiri no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze gusa.
Bitandukanye n'ingamba zabanje, izi ngamba zahagaritswe zashyizweho n'abapolisi, harimo gucibwa amande no gutatanya abantu.
Ibigo byinshi byasabwe gufunga, uretse ibigo byemewe nk'ibikenewe cyane, harimo amasupamaketi, amaduka y'imiti, amabanki, amaduka akora ku giti cye, sitasiyo za lisansi n'amagaraji.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko arwaye COVID-19 yemejwe mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika, muri Leta ya Washington, mu mugabo wari watashye avuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'abakozi ba White House ku cyorezo cya Coronavirus ryashinzwe ku wa 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu buzima bw'abaturage, kandi bushyiraho amategeko abuza abagenzi baturutse mu Bushinwa kwinjira.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara, ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, cyatangaje ko cyateguye igikoresho cyacyo cyo gupima.
Nubwo byari bimeze bityo, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatinze gutangiza ibizamini, bituma umubare nyakuri w'icyorezo icyo gihe utagaragara.
Ibizamini byarakomerekejwe n'ibikoresho by'ipimisha byatunganyijwe na leta muri Gashyantare, nta cyizere leta y'igihugu yari ifite ku bikoresho by'ipimisha bitagengwa na leta (amashuri makuru, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare, ndetse n'ibipimo by'ibanze byo kwemeza gupimwa kugeza mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe (bituma hakenewe ko muganga atanga amabwiriza nyuma yaho).
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru The Washington Post cyatangaje ko muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hakorewe ibizamini bitarenga 4.000.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hateganyijwe ibizamini bitarenga 14 000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso n'amabwiriza ya muganga bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi yo gupimwa. Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika rwamenyekanye muri Leta ya Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukungu, ibyo bikaba byakurikiwe n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yari afunze. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Amerika yamenyeshejwe uko icyorezo cya coronavirus kizahindura igihugu cyayo n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo bo muri kaminuza ya Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko rivuga ko Coronavirus yiteguye kandi ko igomba gukemurwa, ryashyizeho inkunga y'amadolari miliyari 8,3 yo gufasha ibigo bya leta guhangana n'icyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho imipaka ku rugendo rw'abakozi bayo, yahagaritse inama, kandi ashishikariza abakozi gukora bari mu rugo.
Ibirori bya siporo n'ibihe by'umwaka byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari ibihano byo kujya mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, usibye Ubwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30 guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yaguye ingamba zigera no mu Bwongereza na Ireland.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukungu gihangayikishije igihugu, bituma hashyirwaho amafaranga ya leta yo guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi byafunze cyangwa bigabanyije amasaha byakoraga muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika mu kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe muri buri ntara 50 na District of Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, abantu 10.700 banduye coronavirus mu mujyi wa New York, bari benshi kurusha umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda abantu kugaragara ko ari byiza kuko imibare y'abandura yariyongereye kuva ku minsi 2.0 ikagera ku minsi 4.7.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe, i New York hemejwe ko hari abantu 32,308 banduye, naho 672 bahitanywe na virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zavuze ko hari abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Ku ya 8 Mata, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hemejwe ko hari abantu 400,335, naho abantu 12,841 barapfuye.
Ku ya 30 Werurwe, binyuze mu itangazamakuru, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Trump, yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu guhana kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwitwa USNS Comfort, bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1.000, bwashyize inkingi mu mujyi wa New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zagize abantu 884 bapfuye bazize coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Muri Leta ya New York, umubare w'abanduye warenze 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. Inzu y'Umukuru w'Igihugu yanenzwe kubera ko yagabanyije ibyago no kugenzura itumanaho mu gutegeka abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza imvugo n'ibitabo bya leta bijyanye n'iyi virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Kwemera muri rusange uburyo Trump yakemuye ikibazo cy'ihungabana byatewe n'amacakubiri.
Bamwe mu bayobozi n'abatanga ibitekerezo muri Amerika banenze Amerika kubera ko ikenera ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi by'ibanze, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, bivuye mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'uburyo ingendo zo mu ndege zikora ryakoreshejwe mu gupima no guhanura uburyo zikwirakwira, ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru cyitwa Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere 2020.
Nk'uko amakuru yo mu mwaka wa 2018 y'Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Inyambukiragutabara abivuga, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo bihugu byagize umubare munini w'abagenzi baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne nabyo byari ahantu hakunzwe cyane ku bantu bavuye i Wuhan.
Bali yabonetse nk'umurwa udafite ubushobozi bwo kwitegura mu mijyi 20 ikunzwe cyane yo mu bihugu by'amahanga, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yabonetse ko ifite ubushobozi bwo kwitegura.
Yavuze ko hakiri byinshi byo kumenya kuri COVID-19 kandi ko Australia izakomeza kugenzura imipaka no gutangaza amakuru mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habayeho ikibazo cy'umutekano w'ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ko imodoka za Leta za Wuhan na Hubei zafatiwe mu kato, ibihugu byinshi byateguye kwimura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi mu karere, cyane cyane binyuze mu ndege z'igihugu cy'inkomoko, ku bw'uruhushya rwatanzwe n'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand, ni bimwe mu bihugu byabanje gutangiza gahunda yo guhungisha abaturage babyo.
Pakisitani yavuze ko itazakura umuturage wayo wese mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuye muri icyo gihugu abaturage 34 cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, hakubiyemo Abanyapolonye bane, Umunyashinwa umwe n'Umuhindi umwe.
Abaturage b'Abanyapolonye, Abashinwa n'Abahinde bageze muri Polonye, aho indege y'Abanyarabu yahagaritse urugendo mbere yo gukomeza urugendo yerekeza muri Brezili.
Abaturage ba Brazil bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare hafi ya Brasília.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 (176 mu ndege ya mbere na 39 mu ndege ya kabiri yari yaraguzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bakuwe i Wuhan bajya muri BFC Trenton kugira ngo bajye mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 bavuye i Wuhan yageze ku kibuga cya BFC Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Australia bakuye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 Gashyantare, babajyana mu kigo cyo gufungirwamo ku kirwa cya Christmas, cyahindutse ahantu ho kuba mu kato, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Indege yo guhungisha abantu yo muri Nouvelle-Zélande yageze i Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (by'umwihariko baturutse muri Australia na Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cy'abasirikare b'ingabo cya Whangaparaoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zizakura Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bavuye mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, mu ntara ya Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubuhinde yatangiye guhungisha abaturage bayo bavuye muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yakodeshejwe na leta ya Afurika y'Epfo yafashe abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Mbere yo kugenda, hakorewe isuzuma ry'ubuvuzi, kandi abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus bagumye aho bari kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abaturage ba Afurika y'Epfo bageragejwe nabi ni bo bonyine basubijwe mu gihugu.
Ibyavuye mu igerageza byemereye Abanyafurika y'Epfo bose, harimo abasare, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bose bakaba bagumye mu rwego rwo kwirinda, bagumye mu bugenzuzi no mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bari muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bahuriye hamwe kugira ngo batange imfashanyo mu bice by'Ubushinwa byibasiwe na virusi, hamwe n'itsinda ry'abashyize hamwe bo mu karere ka Chicago, bavuga ko batanze udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa N95 mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku wa 30 Mutarama. Ishyirahamwe ry'ubutabazi Direct Relief, rifatanyije na FedEx, ryohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho byo kurinda umuntu, harimo n'intoki n'imyenda, ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union ku wa 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya OMS yo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku rukingo no kuvura no kurinda abantu bari mu kaga muri Afurika no mu Majyepfo ya Aziya.
Interaksyon yatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200.000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapore yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe i Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje ko yatanze imyenda y'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo imyenda ya Hazmat 10.000, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, kandi zasezeranya inkunga y'amafaranga y'amadolari y'Amerika miliyoni 100 ku bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo. Mu gihe ibibazo by'abandura mu Bushinwa byasaga n'ibyasubiranye, icyo gihugu cyohereje imfashanyo mu bihugu byinshi byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke zo gufasha Ubutaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byagenewe gupima abantu miliyoni 1, imyenda yo kwirinda abantu miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro yo kwirinda abantu ibihumbi 60 i Addis Abeba muri Ethiopia, kugira ngo bitangirwe n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bwa Afurika.
Nyuma yaho yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho bitanu byo guhumeka muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque byagaragaje impungenge ku bigunira n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima coronavirus byakozwe mu Bushinwa bifite 30% gusa by'ukuri, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwakuye 600 000 by'amasikini yo mu Bushinwa afite amakosa.
U Bubiligi bwasabye abantu gutaha udupfukamunwa 100.000 tutakiri mu bubiko, twibwira ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'Ubushinwa bwakiriwe neza mu bihugu bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika.Ku wa 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubufasha by'ubutabazi mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga z'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa mu gucunga no guhagarika iki cyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga guhisha ibyo bari bakoze bigatuma imihati yo kwirinda no gukumira iki cyorezo idakorwa, n'icyorezo cyo muri iki gihe aho guverinoma nkuru yatanze raporo buri gihe kugira ngo hatagira ubwoba ku mugoroba w'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu cyo guhagarika ingendo muri Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo atari inama y'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS), ariko ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cy'uko biyemeje gukumira icyorezo aho cyiganje cyane, avuga ko ari ikintu kitari cyigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange. Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemezwa kw'ikwirakwizwa ry'umuntu ku wundi mu Bushinwa no kwiyongera kw'abandura mu bindi bihugu, OMS yavuze ko icyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mpuzamahanga (IHPA), icyakomeje gukemurwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya grippe cya APPI kuva mu 2009.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom yavuze ko ISPPI iterwa n'ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make n'ibifite amafaranga ari hagati, bidakoresha uburyo bwiza bwo kwita ku buzima.
Mu gusubiza ku iyubahirizwa ry'imihango yo kugendera mu mahanga, Tedros yavuze ko:  nta mpamvu yo kugira ngo ingamba zihagarike ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga  kandi  OMS ntishishimiye ko hagira ikumira ku bucuruzi n'ingendo .
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira ibihugu bifite amikoro make mu kwitegura, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gushyigikira ibihugu bitagira uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, nubwo yaba igiye kugaragara.
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko dukomeye nk'aho turi mu gice gikennye  maze asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga  gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura byinshi ejo . Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS yashyizeho mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru ko iyi ndwara yitwa COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni António Guterres yemeye gushyira imbaraga z'umuryango w'abibumbye wose mu gisubizo.
Ishami rya ONU ry'ubuyobozi bw'ibibazo ryashyizweho, kugira ngo rishobore guhuza ibisubizo byose by'umuryango w'abibumbye, ibi bikaba bizatuma OMS ikomeza kwibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuzima mu gihe izindi nzego zizabasha gutanga ubuhanga mu gucunga ingaruka rusange z'icyorezo ku baturage, ubukungu n'iterambere.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'ubutumwa bufatanyije riyobowe na OMS ryatangijwe mu Bushinwa kugira ngo ryohereze impuguke mpuzamahanga na OMS mu Bushinwa kugira ngo bashyigikire imiyoborere y'igihugu no gusuzuma  uburemere n'ikwirakwira ry'iyo ndwara  binyuze mu gutegura amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego zikomeye z'igihugu no gukora ingendo mu gihugu mu rwego rwo gusuzuma  ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza mu ntara no mu turere, harimo mu mijyi no mu cyaro . Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yavuze ko  isi igomba gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus , igaragaza ko nubwo ari kare cyane kuvuga iby'icyorezo, buri gihugu gikwiye kwinjira mu cyiciro cyo kwitegura .
Mu gusubiza icyorezo cya Iran, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abakozi ba OMS muri Irani kugira ngo basuzume uko ibintu byifashe. Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko isuzuma ry'ibyago by'icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi ryavuye kuri "risumba ibindi" rigera kuri "risumba ibindi", ari na ryo shami ry'ibanze ry'ibyavuzwe mu itangazamakuru.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda ya WHO yo gucunga ibibazo by'ubuzima by'ibihe bidasanzwe, yatanze umuburo mu itangazo ati: "Ibi ni ukugaruka ku kuri kuri kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: muhaguruke".
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi ugomba kwitegura, yongeraho ko ingamba zo gusubiza neza zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda icyakabije.
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu atemerera abayobozi b'ubuzima rusange gutangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko kuvuga ko ari icyorezo byumvikanisha ko twemera byimazeyo ko buri muntu wese ku isi ashobora kwandura iyi virusi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora kwitwa icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS ifite impungenge zikomeye z'ibipimo biteye ubwoba by'ikwirakwira n'uburemere ndetse n'ibipimo biteye ubwoba by'ubushomeri. OMS yahuye n'ibitekerezo bikomeye ku bijyanye no gucunga iki cyorezo, byafashwe nk'ibidakwiye, cyane cyane kubera gutangaza hakiri kare ko ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi muri pandemic.
Iki cyemezo cy'uko nta kibazo gihari cyatewe n'impapuro zisaba umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, gutanga imihoho, zashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu za ONU z'ibanze zashimangiye ko uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bugomba kubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo guhabwa ubufasha bwo gutabara, kandi ko ubwo burenganzira ari ubwa leta.
Itsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'uburwayi bitagomba na rimwe kuba urwitwazo rwo kurobanura ku butoni ku bantu runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abafite ubumuga buke, abageze mu za bukuru, abahunze, abatagira aho baba, abakennye cyane, abafunzwe, impunzi n'andi matsinda atazwi akeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ishinzwe ubutegetsi iri kwita ku ngaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage ziterwa n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'ubufatanye mu by'ubukungu no guteza imbere watangije urubuga rutanga amakuru ajyanye n'igihe kandi yuzuye ku bisubizo by'amategeko mu bihugu bitandukanye byo ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Hagati y'amabwiriza yo gukomeza sisitemu z'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi, no gusubiza ingaruka z'ifungwa n'ingendo z'abimukira, urubuga rwa digitale rurimo igikoresho cya Country Policy Tracker kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bindi no koroshya uburyo bw'isi yose bwo guhangana n'ikibazo cya coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Ibiro bya Guverinoma y'u Bwongereza Michael Gove n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brezili Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, ku buryo yayoboye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei yo mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi b'intara benshi b'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa (CCP) bakuwe ku mirimo yabo kubera uburyo bakoresheje mu gushyira abantu mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, mu kugaragaza ko batishimiye uko abayobozi b'ibihugu bakiriye icyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo batekereza ko icyo gikorwa cyari kigamije kurinda Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi bakuru b'Ubushinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze igitekerezo cya mbere cy'uko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira ibitekerezo by'abahuza umugambi w'uko COVID-19 ishobora kuba yarakomotse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika bwise coronavirus virusi y'Ubushinwa cyangwa virusi ya Wuhan, buvuga ko mu Bushinwa, kugenzura byongereye imbaraga virusi y'icyorezo cyugarije isi, nyuma y'aho bamwe mu baturwanya bavuga ko ari ivangura ry'amoko, bigamije guhungabanya abantu ku kuba ubutegetsi bwe budashobora gukumira iyi ndwara.
Ikinyamakuru The Daily Beast cyakiriye telegarama ya leta ya Amerika igaragaza uburyo bwo gutangaza amakuru bwagaragaye ko bwaturutse mu kanama gashinzwe umutekano w'igihugu, aho bavugaga ko ari uko: "byose bituruka mu Bushinwa".
Dusabwa kugerageza kugeza ubwo butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo mu biganiro n'abanyamakuru no ku mateleviziyo. Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byavuze ko imihati y'Ubushinwa yo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa by'imyidagaduro yo gushaka kugira uruhare ku isi.
Umuyobozi w'umushinga w'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi Josep Borrell yaburiye ko hari "ingingo ya politiki y'ubutaka isaba urugamba rw'imbaraga binyuze mu mvugo no mu "politiki y'ubuntu".
Borrell yavuze kandi ko  Ubushinwa bushimangira cyane ko, bitandukanye na Amerika, ari umufasha w'inshingano kandi wizewe .
