Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa isaba ubufasha ku wa 14 Werurwe 2020, avuga ko igihugu cye kigorwa no kurwanya iki cyorezo kubera ko Amerika yafatiye ibihano Irani. Iki cyorezo cyateye Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gusaba ko yakurikiza politiki z'imibereho myiza zisanzwe n'ibindi bihugu bikize, harimo gahunda rusange y'ubuzima, gahunda rusange yo kwita ku bana, ikiruhuko cy'ababyeyi gihemba n'amafaranga menshi yo gushyigikira ubuzima rusange.
Abasesenguzi mu bya politiki biteze ko ibyo bizagira ingaruka mbi ku byiringiro bya Donald Trump byo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya perezida ya 2020.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze  ibikorwa by'ubwirinzi by'abantu gusa  byakozwe n'u Buyapani nyuma y'aho iki gihugu gitangarije ko umuntu wese uzava muri Koreya y'Epfo azashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce twashyizweho na leta.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo mu mizo ya mbere wari waratandukanye ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yakemuye ikibazo cy'ubukene.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon ashinjwa uburyo leta itari ifite uburyo bwo gukemura iki cyorezo cyangwa se ko yashimye uko yabyitwayemo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuze ko ibyo bishobora gutuma ubutegetsi bukomeza ububasha bwabwo.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yemeye ko Minisitiri w'Intebe, Viktor Orbán, ategeka ku bw'itegeko kugeza igihe habonetse andi mabwiriza, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko n'amatora no guhana umuntu wese ushinjwa gukwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma kuri virusi n'uburyo leta ikemura ikibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatewe n'ubushomeri buke, bitewe n'uko ku isi hose hakoreshejwe ibikoresho byinshi mu kurwanya icyorezo, abantu bagura ibintu mu buryo bwo guhungabana, kandi ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikorwaremezo bikangirika.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze imiburo ku kibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi kubera ko abaguzi bakomeje kwiyongera kandi ababikora bakabura ababibasaba.
Hari n'utundi duce twinshi twahuye n'ubuhunzi bw'abantu batinyaga, bituma ibintu by'ibanze bikenera, urugero nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku, amacupa y'amazi, ibishyimbo, bivaho, bituma habaho ubukene.
Urwego rw'ikoranabuhanga, by'umwihariko, rwatangaje ku gutinda kw'ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom, abashaka ibikoresho byo kwirinda ubwabo biyongereye inshuro 100.
Ibi byatumye ibiciro byiyongeraho inshuro 20 z'ibiciro bisanzwe, kandi byanagize ingaruka zo gutinda gutanga ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu gihe cy'amezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
Ibi kandi byatumye ku isi hose habaho ibura ry'ibikoresho byo kwirinda, kandi OMS iraburira ko ibi bizashyira mu kaga abakora mu by'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cyatanze amahirwe mashya ku bacuruzi bagurisha ibicuruzwa byo muri Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Uyu mushinga watumye amata y'abana aba make mu maduka manini amwe n'amwe, nyuma yaho Leta ya Ositaraliya irawuhagarika. Nubwo abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, kandi hakaba hari hakenewe cyane ibiribwa, ibyo bice byombi byarahunze kubera ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zashyizweho n'Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani zo kurwanya ubucakura n'ubucuruzi butemewe bw'ibikoresho by'ibanze zagize icyo zigeraho, bityo bikirinda inzara zikomeye zari zateganyijwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Kubera umusaruro munini w'ubuhinzi, u Butaliyani bw'amajyaruguru ntibwagize igabanuka rikomeye, ariko ibiciro bishobora kuzamuka nk'uko abahagarariye inganda babivuga.
Amafunguro yahagaze ubusa by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi b'Ubushinwa bari bamaze gushyira hanze inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyokurya bihagije.
Amategeko nk'ayo ariho mu Butaliyani kugira ngo abahinzi b'ibiribwa babike ibicuruzwa bya ngombwa mu gihe habaye ibintu nk'ibyo byihutirwa.
Ingaruka mbi ku bukungu bw'isi byibonekeje mu Bushinwa: nk'uko raporo y'itangazamakuru yo ku wa 16 Werurwe ibigaragaza, ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere y'umwaka wa 2020 kubera ingamba zafashwe na leta zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'ibicuruzwa byagabanutseho 20,5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari ikigo gikomeye cy'ubukungu n'inganda, byaragaragaye ko icyorezo cya virusi ari ingorabahizi ikomeye cyane ku bukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo muri Economist Intelligence Unit yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza kuba mabi kugeza igihe hazaba hagiye kugaragara neza ibisubizo by'ibibazo bishobora kuvuka.
Muri Mutarama 2020, hari abasesenguzi bavuze ko ingaruka z'ubukungu bw'iki cyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kurenga izari zitewe n'icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye hagati ya 2002-2004.
Impuguke muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis yavuze ko ingaruka z'amadolari asaga miriyari 300 ku muyoboro w'ibikoresho ku isi zishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Umuryango w'ibihugu by'ubucuruzi bw'ibitoro (OPEC) wavuzwe ko  wacitse  nyuma y'ikena rikomeye ry'ibiciro bya peteroli kubera ibyifuzo by'ubushinwa.
Amasoko y'imari ku isi yose yagabanutse ku ya 24 Gashyantare kubera ubwiyongere bukabije bw'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge zikomeje kwiyongera ku cyorezo cya coronavirus, ibipimo byinshi by'isoko ry'imari muri Amerika birimo NASDAQ-100, S&ampP 500 na Dow Jones Industrial Average byerekanye ibirarane bikomeye cyane kuva mu 2008, aho Dow Jones yagabanutseho amanota 1119, ari na yo yagabanutse cyane mu munsi umwe kuva mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'imari ryo mu 2007-08.
Ibipimo byose uko ari bitatu byarangiye icyumweru bikubye hejuru ya 10%.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje ko inguzanyo ya leta y'u Bushinwa ifite inguzanyo ariko ikomeza kubona ko nta nyungu.
Imigwi yongeye kugwa kubera ubwoba bw'icyorezo cya coronavirus, aho ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe yagabanutse cyane.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu buzagabanuka.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu Mohamed El-Erian yashimye ingamba z'ubutabazi zashyizweho mu gihe gikwiye n'amabanki nkuru n'ibihugu.
Banki nkuru z'igihugu zitabiriye vuba kurusha uko zabyitabiriye mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'imari mu mwaka wa 2008.
Urugendo ni kimwe mu bice byahuye cyane n'ibihano byo gutembera, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, cyane cyane ahantu hakundaga gutemberera ba mukerarugendo, no kuba leta zateye inkunga yo kutanyura mu bihugu byose.
Ku bw'ibyo, kompanyi nyinshi z'indege zataye ingendo kubera ibyifuzo by'abazikenera, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas, mu gihe kompanyi y'indege yo mu Bwongereza Flybe yafunzwe.
Ingaruka ku rugendo rw'ubwato zageze ku rwego rutari rwigeze rubaho mbere.
Sitasiyo nyinshi n'ibibuga by'indege na byo byarafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyabaye mu gihe cya Chunyun, igihe cy'ubukerarugendo gikomeye gihuza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa.
Ibikorwa byinshi by'abantu benshi byasenywe na leta z'igihugu n'iz'akarere, harimo n'ibirori bya buri mwaka byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya, kandi ibigo by'abikorera na byo byafunze amaduka n'ibibanza by'ubukerarugendo, nka Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Ibirori byinshi bifitanye isano n'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi byarahagaritswe, kandi ahantu henshi hatembereye abantu barafunzwe kugira ngo hatabaho guterana kw'abantu benshi, harimo n'Umujyi W'Abatemewe wa Beijing n'amasoko gakondo y'urusengero.
Mu ntara 24, mu mirenge n'uturere 31 byo mu Bushinwa, abategetsi bongereye iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Gashyantare, basaba ko ahantu henshi ho gukoreramo imirimo hatagomba gufungura mbere y'uko uwo munsi ugera.
