Ibi kandi byatumye urujya n'uruza rw'abantu mu maduka rumanuka hagati ya 33 na 43% muri Werurwe ugereranyije na Gashyantare.
Abakora ibigo by'ubucuruzi ku isi hose bashyizeho ingamba z'inyongera, nko kongera inshuro zo gusukura, gushyiraho ibikoresho bya tekiniki bya tekiniki y'ubushyuhe kugira ngo barebe ubushyuhe bw'abakiriya no guhagarika ibirori. Nk'uko Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Epfo igaragaza, icyorezo cyateje ubukene gishobora gutuma abantu bari hagati ya miliyoni 14 na 22 baba mu bukene bukabije muri Amerika y'Epfo ugereranyije n'aho hatari icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe icyorezo cyari cyiganje i Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi.
Muri u Bushinwa, abenshi mu bakozi b'abimukira bagera kuri miriyoni 300 bavuye mu cyaro, baheze mu ngo zabo mu ntara zo hagati cyangwa mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miriyoni 10 batakaje akazi maze basaba leta ubufasha.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gutwara imirimo miliyoni 47 muri Amerika, kandi ubushomeri bushobora kugera kuri 32% nkuko bitangazwa na Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis. Gufunga mu Buhinde byatumye miliyoni nyinshi z'abakozi b'abimukira b'Abahinde (babona umushahara w'umunsi) babura akazi. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cya Angus Reid bwabonye ko 44% by'ingo za Canada zahuye n'ubushomeri bw'uburyo runaka. Abakozi bagera ku 900,000 batakaje akazi muri Esipanye kuva mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020.
Mu gice cya kabiri cya Werurwe, abakozi b'Abafaransa bagera kuri miliyoni 4 basabye inguzanyo y'ubushomeri bw'agateganyo, naho abakozi b'Abongereza bagera kuri miliyoni 1 basaba inguzanyo rusange.
Gahunda y'ubudehe mu Budage yashyizweho n'Ubufaransa n'Ubwongereza.
