Imiryango ikora mu by'ubuhanzi n'umuco yagerageje gukomeza inshingano yayo (ikunda gushyigikirwa na Leta) yo guha abaturage uburenganzira bwo kubona umurage w'umuco, kubungabunga umutekano w'abakozi bayo n'abaturage no gushyigikira abahanzi aho bishoboka.
Muri Werurwe 2020, ku isi hose no mu byiciro bitandukanye, amazu ndangamurage, amabaruwa, amazu y'imyidagaduro n'izindi nzego z'umuco byafunzwe kugeza igihe hatangarijwe ibindi, kandi imurika ryayo, ibyabaye n'ibyagarutsweho byakuweho cyangwa byimuriwe.
