Kimwe na Diyosezi Gatolika y'i Roma yafunze insengero zayo n'amasengero yayo, ndetse na St. Peter's Square irirukana abagenzi bose b'Abakristo, izindi nzego z'amadini na zo zahagaritse ibikorwa byazo kandi zihagarika amateraniro rusange mu nsengero, mu misigiti, mu masinagogi, mu nsengero no mu gurdwaras.
Minisitiri w'Ubuzima wa Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu yasubitswe mu bice byibasiwe n'icyorezo, kandi ko ahantu hatagatifu hafunzwe, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abanyamahanga n'abaturage bayo kwinjira mu bibanza bitagatifu bya Mecca na Medina.
