Gupima muri laboratwari indwara ya coronavirus yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano birimo uburyo bwo gupima virusi no gupima udukoko tw'umubiri twakozwe mu gihe cy'ubwandu.
Virusi mu bipimo byemezwa na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Iyi myitozo yagenewe cyane cyane kureba gusa RNA ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu buherutse cyangwa bukiriho.
Gushakisha antibody (serology) birashobora gukoreshwa mu gupima no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo bitagomba kumenyekana cyangwa abantu badafite ibimenyetso.
Igiciro cy'urupfu rw'indwara n'urwego rw'ubwirinzi bw'urugaga mu baturage bishobora kwemezwa hakurikijwe ibipimo by'iyi test.
Kubera gupima ku rugero ruciriritse, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku bijyanye n'umubare w'abanduye virusi mu baturage muri Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoze ibizamini birenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini ku mubare w'ibizamini byakozwe mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Ibi bishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku mibare y'abapfa, ishobora kuba yaragaragajwe cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo guhindura imiterere y'umubiri hakurikijwe uburyo bwo gukora polymerisation mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR), iki kizamini gishobora gukorwa ku bipimo byo mu mwuka byafashwe hakoreshejwe uburyo butandukanye, harimo ikinyamushongo cyo mu mazuru cyangwa icyuma cyo mu kanwa.
Ibisubizo bikunze kuboneka mu masaha make kugeza ku minsi ibiri.
Iperereza rya RT-PCR rikorewe ku bipimo by'ibinyamushongo ni ryo riringirwa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ishobora kuva mu muhogo mu gihe ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bapimwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, bashobora no gukusanywa mu nzira zo mu nda bakoresheje uburyo bwo guhumeka, cyangwa bakanywera (bakanyura) mu kanwa.
Kimwe mu bipimo bya mbere bya PCR cyakozwe na Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 hifashishijwe imikorere yo guhindura imiterere y'ibinyabuzima hakurikijwe uburyo bwo gukora polymerisation mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR), kikaba ari cyo cyatumye haboneka ibikoresho 250 000 byatanzwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwari bwakoze ikizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020.Sosiyete yo muri Koreya y'Epfo yitwa Kogenebiotech yakoze igikoresho cyo gupima SARS-CoV-2 cy'icyiciro cya muganga gishingiye kuri PCR (PowerChek Coronavirus) ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Igerageza kubona ingirabuzima fatizo E  ihuriyeho na virusi ya corona beta yose, n'ingirabuzima fatizo RdRp ihuriyeho na SARS-CoV-2.Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni imwe mu sosiyete za mbere zahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa na Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ibijyanye n'imiti mu Bushinwa mu ikoranabuhanga rya PCR mu gupima SARS-CoV-2.Mu Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga ibikoresho byo gupima virusi ya corona 2019 (2019-nCoV) hakoreshejwe RT-PCR mu gihe nyacyo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi binyuze mu ikoranabuhanga rya International Reagent Resource.
Mu byiciro by'ibikoresho by'igerageza bya kera, kimwe muri bitatu by'igerageza ry'ibinyabuzima cyagaragazaga ibisubizo bitagira icyo byemeza kubera ibikoresho bitagira ingano, ndetse n'ikibazo cyo gupima mu kigo cya CDC cyo muri Atlanta. Ibyo byatumye mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare 2020 hafatwa ibipimo biri munsi ya 100 ku munsi.
Ibipimo bikoresha ibice bibiri ntibyari byitezwe ko ari byo byiringirwa kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, ari na bwo laboratoire za leta n'iz'ibanze zahawe uburenganzira bwo gutangira gupima.
Iki kizamini cyemejwe n'Ikigo cy'Ubuyobozi bw'Ibiribwa n'Imiti ku bw'Inyandiko y'Itegeko ry'Ubukangurambaga. Ibigo by'ubuziranenge byo muri Amerika byatangiye gupima mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020.
