Amazi n'inzoga bica mikorobe, mikorobe zidakira indwara nyinshi (SARM na ERV), igituntu, na za virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi itera SIDA, herpes, virusi ya RSV, virusi ya rhinovirus, urukingo, ibicurane na hepatite), kimwe n'imishishi.
