Gukaraba intoki mu mazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Amazi y'amazi ni yo akwiriye kubera ko ashobora kwanduza amazi adafite amazi, naho ubushyuhe bw'amazi ntibugaragarira ko ari bwo butuma habaho itandukaniro).
Gushyira isabune nyinshi ku biganza, ubisiga ku biganza, kandi ntuzibagirwe ku biganza, hagati y'intoki no munsi y'imisumari.
Isabuni ikura udukoko mu ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakunda gukaraba intoki neza cyane iyo bakoresheje isabune kurusha amazi yonyine.
Gushyiraho nibura amasegonda 20.
Gukata bituma habaho guhuzagurika, bigatuma udukoko dukurwa mu ruhu, kandi gukata igihe kirekire birakuraho udukoko twinshi.
Jya ukaraba neza mu mazi.
Gukaraba mu ibesani y'amazi adakama bishobora gutuma intoki zikongera kwanduzwa.
Gutakaza n'igitambaro gitunganye cyangwa mu kirere.
Ibice bikunze kwirengagizwa ni ikiganza cy'iburyo, intoki, hagati y'intoki n'amaboko.
Amagi y'ibishushanyo n'amabara y'iminwa ashobora kubamo udukoko duto cyane.
Ubusanzwe, umuti wo gusiga amazi mu ntoki ni wo utuma umuntu atagira intoki zikomotse; iyo uruhu rukomeye bituma habaho ibikomere ku ruhu bishobora kongera ibyago byo kwanduza indwara.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo gukaraba intoki mu gihe amazi y'amazi ya rubanda n'isabune ataboneka. Urugero, gutemba amazi mu bikoresho by'amazi cyangwa mu bikoresho by'amazi by'ibumba n'ibindi, cyangwa gukoresha ivu iyo bikenewe, mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Mu mimerere aho amazi aba ari make (nk'amashuri cyangwa uturere two mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari uburyo bwo kubungabunga amazi, nko gukoresha utuzi n'ubundi buryo bw'ubukungu.
Ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho by'amazi ni iryoroheje rikoresha inkono itegetswe ku mugozi, n'ikinyururu cyo ku mukono gitanga amazi make ku biganza n'umugati w'isabune.
Kumesa intoki neza ni igice cy'ingenzi mu mikorere yo kugira isuku y'intoki, ariko uburyo bwiza bwo kumesa intoki mu bwiherero bwa rubanda buracyari impaka.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bugaragaza ko utwo dupapuro ari two dufite isuku kurusha utwo dukarabya dukoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki dukoreshwa n'amashanyarazi, dukunze kuboneka mu bwiherero.
Mu 2008, ubushakashatsi bwatewe inkunga n'inganda z'impapuro z'ipamba, European Tissue Symposium, bwakorewe muri Kaminuza ya Westminster, mu mujyi wa Londres, hagamijwe kugereranya ibipimo by'isuku byatanzwe n'amasahani y'impapuro, imashini zimesa intoki z'umwuka ushyushye n'imashini zimesa intoki z'umwuka.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no gukaraba intoki mu gikomoro cy'umwuka ushyushye, byagaragaye ko umubare w'udukoko twanduye wiyongereyeho 194 ku ijana ku kigero ku ntoki no ku biganza 254 ku ijana.
Kumesa intoki hakoreshejwe umwuka byatumye umubare w'udukoko twanduye ku munwa wiyongeraho 42%, ku biganza wiyongeraho 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki hakoreshejwe umwenda w'impapuro, umubare w'udukoko wari ugabanutseho 76 ku ijana ku kigero ku munwa w'intoki, ndetse ugera kuri 77 ku ijana ku biganza. Abahanga mu bya siyansi bakoze kandi ibizamini kugira ngo bamenye niba hari ubushobozi bwo kwanduzanya n'abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'ibidukikije by'ubwiherero bitewe n'uburyo bw'umwuma.
Ikirahuri cy'amazi cyo kumesa intoki, gihumeka umwuka mu gikoresho ku muvuduko wavuzwe wa 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), gishobora kwirukana mikorobe mu ntoki no mu gikoresho, kandi gishobora kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero ndetse n'ibidukikije by'ubwiherero mu kirere cya metero 2.
Gukoresha umujyo wo gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umwuka ushyushye bituma mikorobe zishobora gukwirakwira mu ntera ya metero 0.25 uvuye ku umujyo wo gukaraba intoki.
Mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, bwagaragaje uburyo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, habonetse impinduka zikurikira mu mibare y'ibinyabuzima:
Hari abahanga benshi batandukanye bakora imashini zo kumesa intoki, kandi imashini zo kumesa intoki zagereranyijwe no kumesa hakoreshejwe amasahani.
Gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe udupfukamunwa twanduza indwara ni ubundi buryo bwo guhanagura mu gihe umuntu ari mu ngendo, mu gihe nta sabuni n'amazi.
Amavuta y'inzoga agomba kuba afite nibura 60% by'inzoga.
Gukaraba intoki mu bitaro byabaye itegeko nyuma y'igihe kirekire umuganga w'Umuhongiriya witwa Ignaz Semmelweis avumbuye ko ari ingirakamaro mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro (mu wa 1846).
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bivuga ko abakozi bo mu bitaro bibagirwa gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukoresha izo nkingo byagabanyije umubare w'abandura.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi bigomba kumara nibura amasegonda 15, ukoresheje isabune nyinshi n'amazi cyangwa gel mu kumesa no gukaraba buri gice cy'intoki.
Ibiganza bigomba gukubitwa hagati y'intoki.
Niba hari ibisigazwa munsi y'iminwa, ushobora gukoresha umufuka wo gukaraba imisatsi kugira ngo ubikureho.
Kubera ko mikorobe ziri mu mazi zishobora kuguma ku biganza, ni ngombwa ko ukaraba neza kandi ukayihanaguza n'utwo dupfukamunwa.
Nyuma yo gukama, igikoresho cy'impapuro kigomba gukoreshwa mu gufunga amazi (kandi gufungura urugi rw'ibiro iyo bibaye ngombwa).
Ibyo bituma umuntu atongera kwanduza intoki ze iyo ari ku butaka.
Intego yo gukaraba intoki mu bigo nderabuzima ni ukuvanaho udukoko dutera indwara ( udukoko ) no kwirinda ko twanduzwa.
Ikinyamakuru The New England Journal of Medicine kivuga ko mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, abantu batakomeje gukaraba intoki mu buryo bukwiriye, kubera ko abaganga benshi n'abaforomo bakunda kwibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi babo, ibyo bikaba bituma mikorobe zitandura.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza no gukurikiza ubundi buryo bworoshye bishobora kugabanya ku kigero cya 66 ku ijana ubwandu bw'amaraso buturuka ku gutambagira intoki.
Inyandiko y'amabwiriza y'isuku y'amaboko yashyizweho n'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishobora kandi gusomwa ku rubuga rwa interineti kugira ngo abantu bayagireho ibitekerezo.
Ubushakashatsi bukwiriye bwakozwe na Whitby et al.
Ibikoresho biboneka mu bucuruzi bishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'amaboko, niba byemejwe ko hakurikijwe amategeko.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) washyizeho indangagaciro eshanu z'isuku y'amaboko:
nyuma yo kwanduzwa amaraso/imiti;
mbere yo gukora ingendo zo kwirinda;
Nyuma yo kuvugana n'umurwayi, kongeramo imiti yo kurwanya udukoko mu isabune (sabune "y'imiti" cyangwa "irwanya mikorobe") bituma umuti wo gukaraba intoki urimbura udukoko.
Ni byiza ko iyi mikorobe ikurwaho mbere yo kubagwa cyangwa mu bidukikije aho hari udukoko twangiza umuti wa antibiotique. Kugira ngo umuntu 'akwice' intoki mu gihe cyo kubagwa, bisaba ko agira akuma ashobora gufungura no gufunga atiriwe akoresha intoki, umuti wo gukaraba urimo chlorhexidine cyangwa iode, utwo twuma twuma tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe tumwe, umufuka udakoreshwa imiti y'ubumara mu gihe cyo gukaraba, n'ikindi gikoresho kidakoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki.
Inzu zose z'umurimbo zigomba kuvanwamo.
Muri ubu buryo, ni ngombwa ko umuntu akaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku nkokora, ubusanzwe mu gihe cy'iminota 2 kugeza kuri 6.
Si ngombwa ko umuntu asukura intoki mu gihe cy'iminota 10.
Mu gihe ukaraba, ugomba kwirinda ko amazi ari ku biganza byawe agera ku biganza byawe.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, ni byiza gukaraba intoki ukoresheje igitambaro cy'ubumara kandi ukambara ikoti y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo udukoko dutangire gukwirakwira, ni byiza ko umuntu yakaraba intoki cyangwa agakoresha umuti wo kugabanya ubukana bw'ibicurane mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Ku bijyanye no kugenzura indwara z'indwara z'ibicurane mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu nyinshi zo gukaraba intoki zibonetse mu 20% ya mbere yo gukaraba, kandi ko hari inyungu nke cyane z'inyongera zo kongera inshuro zo gukaraba intoki zirenze 35%.
Iyo ugereranyije gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune isanzwe n'iyo ukoresheje isabune irwanya mikorobe, usanga indwara zandura zandura zituruka ku mikorobe zanduzwa n'ibiribwa zikuba inshuro zirenga eshatu. Mu buryo nk'ubwo, ugereranyije gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umuti urimo inzoga n'ukunywa isabune irwanya mikorobe mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 buri kimwe, usanga uburyo bwa mbere bugabanya ubwandu bwa mikorobe ku kigero cya 26% ugereranyije n'ubw'ubu.
Ariko isabune n'amazi ni byo bifasha cyane kurusha inzoga mu kugabanya virusi ya grippe A (H1N1) na Clostridium difficile ku ntoki. Mu rwego rwo kunoza isuku y'amaboko mu bigo nderabuzima, harimo kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, kubashyiramo inzoga nyinshi no kubamenyesha mu nyandiko no mu magambo.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwimbitse kugira ngo hamenyekane uburyo bwiza bwo kuvura mu bigo bitandukanye by'ubuzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni uburyo buhendutse kandi bw'ingenzi bwo gukomeza kugira ubuzima bwiza, ndetse no kugira ibyokurya byiza.
Ariko kandi, kubera ko nta mazi meza, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu rugo, ku ishuri no ku kazi, ntibyoroshye gushyiraho amahame mpuzamahanga yo kugira isuku y'intoki.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'Afurika yo mu cyaro, kubona amasoko yo gukaraba intoki hafi y'ubwiherero bwa bwite cyangwa bwa leta ni gake, nubwo hari uburyo bworoheje bwo kubaka aho bakaraza intoki.
Nyamara, umubare muke w'abantu bakaraba intoki ushobora kuba uterwa n'imyitwarire y'abantu, aho kuba uterwa n'ibura ry'isabune cyangwa amazi.
Guteza imbere gukaraba intoki n'isabune no gukora ibikorwa byo kubimenyekanisha bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ya politiki, kumenyekanisha inyungu z'iyo myitwarire no guhindura imyitwarire y'abaturage mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bigerweho, hakenewe ibikorwa byo gukurikirana no gupima.
Igenzura ry'ubushakashatsi 70 ryagaragaje ko uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'agati, bwungutse mu kongera umubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki, naho gahunda zo kwamamaza ku buryo bw'imibereho myiza zikananira. Ku birebana no guteza imbere gukaraba intoki mu mashuri, urugero ni "Inzira y'Inyenyeri eshatu" ya UNICEF, ishishikariza amashuri gushyiraho ingamba zoroshye kandi zitahenze zo kureba ko abanyeshuri bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune, ariko bakita no ku yindi mico myiza.
Iyo amashuri ageze ku bipimo by'ibanze, ashobora kuva ku nyenyeri imwe ajya ku zindi eshatu.
Kubaka aho bakaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo guteza imbere isuku y'intoki bigamije kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi Mpuzamahanga wo Gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bugamije guteza imbere imyitwarire. Nyuma y'icyorezo cya Coronavirus cya 2019-2020, UNICEF yashishikarije abantu gukoresha ishusho ya emoji igaragaza gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwarebye ku gaciro k'amafaranga yo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere ugereranyije n'umubare w'imyaka y'ubuzima buzira umuze umuntu ashobora kunguka (ni ukuvuga DALY zirinzwe).
Ariko kandi, hari ikinyamakuru cyavuze ko guteza imbere gukaraba intoki hakoreshejwe isabune ari byo byunguka amafaranga menshi kurusha ibindi bikorwa by'amazi n'isuku.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu, cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibibazo nk'ababyeyi bavuka cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro, bwa mbere kabonetse hagati mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abapayiniya babiri mu by'isuku y'intoki: umuganga w'Umuhungari Ignaz Semmelweis wakoraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya na Florence Nightingale, washinze ubuforomo bugezweho mu Bwongereza.
Icyo gihe, abantu benshi bari bagikeka ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi zitwa miasms.
Mu myaka ya za 80, indwara z'ibyorezo zituruka ku biribwa n'indwara zandura mu bitaro byatumye ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitera inkunga cyane isuku y'amaboko nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Igitero cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye mu bihugu byinshi abantu barushaho kumenya ko ari ngombwa gukaraba intoki n'isabune kugira ngo birinde indwara zandura.
Urugero, mu Budage, ibyapa byerekana uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki byashyizwe iruhande rw'ibikoresho byo gukaraba mu ngo za leta, mu mazu y'ibiro n'ahandi hantu ho gukaraba ku bibuga by'indege.
Imvugo  gukaraba intoki  yerekeza ku muntu wanga kwemera inshingano cyangwa kuba mu bufatanyacyaha bw'ikintu runaka.
Iryo jambo ryakomotse ku murongo wo muri Bibiliya wa Matayo, uvuga ukuntu Ponsiyo Pilato yiyuhagira amaboko igihe yafataga umwanzuro wo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko iryo jambo ryakwirakwiriye cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe by'Icyongereza.
Mu gitabo cya Shakespeare cyitwa Macbeth, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki ku gahato kugira ngo agerageze gukaraba ikizinga cyo mu bwenge, ikimenyetso cy'umutimanama we mubi ku byaha yakoze kandi akaburira umugabo we gukora.
Byongeye kandi, byagaragaye ko abantu bamwe na bamwe, nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza gukora ibikorwa bidakwiriye, bakunda gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, kandi bakishimira cyane ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kugira ibitekerezo nk'ibyo, ntibakunda gukora ibindi bikorwa byo kwiyeza, urugero nko gukora umurimo w'ubwitange.
Amadini amwe n'amwe ategeka ko umuntu akaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku no mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, ni ugukoresha amazi aho gukoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki, ni kimwe mu birori byo gukaraba intoki byashyizwe imbere mu madini menshi, harimo idini rya Baha'i n'iry'Abahindu, kwibiza (tevilah) no gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'umugenzo (Netilat Yadayim) mu idini ry'Abayahudi, lavbo mu Bukristo na wudhu muri Islam. Amadini ategeka kandi ko umuntu akaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku, cyane cyane nyuma y'ibikorwa bimwe na bimwe.
Dukurikije idini ry'Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abayisilamu, ni ngombwa ko umuntu akaraba intoki nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, idini ry'Abahindu, iry'Ababuda, iry'Abasiki, iry'Abayahudi n'iry'Abisilamu, na ryo risaba ko umuntu akaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kurya.
Igenzura ry'ibyago bya COVID-19 ku kazi
Kugenzura ibyago bya COVID-19 ku kazi bisobanura gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyago mu kazi hagamijwe kwirinda indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura ibyago bihagije mu kazi biratandukanye bitewe n'aho ukorera n'imirimo, hashingiwe ku gupima ibyago by'ibanze by'ubwandu, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage n'ibyago by'umuntu ku giti cye ku bakozi bashobora kuba bafite ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA) muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, imirimo ifite ibyago bike byo kwandura ifata umwanya muto mu kazi, aho usanga ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura ari zo zonyine zisabwa, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kwirinda guhumeka no gukomeza isuku no kwirinda indwara mu kazi.
Imirimo ifite ibyago byo kwandura by'umurengera ikubiyemo imirimo isaba ko umuntu yakorana kenshi cyangwa yahurira hafi n'abantu badafite COVID-19 bakekwaho cyangwa bazwiho, ariko bashobora kwandura kubera ko abantu bakwirakwiza iyo virusi mu baturage cyangwa se kubera ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibi birimo abakozi bahuye n'abaturage muri rusange cyane cyane mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo imirimo myinshi hamwe na bimwe mu bice by'ubucuruzi bifite umubare munini w'abantu.
Mu buyobozi bw'ibyago muri iri tsinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo guhumeka ukoresheje imyanda ikora neza cyane, amadirishya meza, no gutanga ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umuntu ku giti cye mu gihe ahuye n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakora mu mirimo y'ihamba bagaragarijwe abantu bakekwaho cyangwa bazwiho COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, bakajya mu byorezo byinshi cyane mu gihe bakora ibikorwa byo gukora aerosol cyangwa gufata cyangwa gukoresha ibipimo by'abantu bakekwaho cyangwa bazwiho COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'ibyago bikwiye ku bakozi nk'abo birimo ibipimo bya tekiniki nk'ibyumba by'umuyaga w'umuvuduko mubi n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bikwiye ku kazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batari mu kazi kubera ko barwaye, bagomba kwita ku bandi cyangwa batinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Uburyo bwo gukora ubucuruzi bushobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibicuruzwa bisabwa ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubikura (urugero nko kugura hanze y'amasaha y'ikiruhuko cyangwa gukoresha serivisi zo gutanga cyangwa gutwara abantu).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibikoresho bivuye mu turere twugarijwe cyane na COVID-19 bishobora guhagarikwa. Gahunda yo kwitegura indwara zandura no kuyikemura ishobora gukoreshwa nk'ubuyobozi bw'ingamba zo kwirinda.
Amategeko agenga ingamba zo kwirinda indwara ziterwa n'imikorere y'umubiri, hamwe n'imikorere y'umubiri, ni yo igomba gufatwa nk'ingamba zo kwirinda indwara ziterwa n'imikorere y'umubiri.
Nanone kandi, bagaragaza uburyo bwo kugenzura kugira ngo bakemure ibyo bibazo, kandi bagashyiraho gahunda z'ubutabazi mu gihe habaye icyorezo.
Gutegura no gusubiza mu buryo ku ndwara zandura bishobora gushyirwa mu nama z'igihugu cyangwa z'akarere.
Intego zo gusubiza icyorezo zirimo kugabanya ikwirakwira mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bice by'imitangire yabo.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu muryango aho ikigo giherereye bufite ingaruka ku bisubizo byatanzwe.
Urutonde rw'ibyangombwa by'ibyago ni uburyo bukoreshwa mu rwego rw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi mu rwego rwo gushyira hamwe ibyangombwa by'ibyago hakurikijwe uko bikora.
Iyo ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora kuvanwaho, uburyo bwiza bwo kugenzura ni ubuhanga, hakurikiraho kugenzura mu rwego rw'ubuyobozi, hanyuma hakagirwa ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
Igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga risobanura kurinda abakozi ibyago by'akazi, ariko ntirigomba gushingira ku myitwarire y'abakozi.
Igenzura ry'ubuyobozi ryerekeza ku mpinduka mu miyoborere cyangwa mu mikorere ku kazi, bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ubwigenge bw'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) bufatwa nk'ubudafite ingufu nyinshi ugereranyije n'ubushakashatsi bw'ikoranabuhanga n'ubw'ubuyobozi, ariko bushobora gufasha mu gukumira ibyangijwe bimwe na bimwe.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa hakurikijwe akaga ku mukozi, bugakoreshwa neza mu gihe bikenewe (urugero: udupfukamunwa two guhumeka), bukambara neza kandi buri gihe, bugasuzumwa buri gihe, bugakoreshwa neza kandi bushyirwa mu mwanya wa mbere igihe bikenewe, kandi bukurwaho neza, bukisukura kandi bugashyingurwa cyangwa bugasubikwa mu buryo bukwiriye kugira ngo birinde kwanduzwa.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA) muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, imirimo ifite ibyago bike byo kwandura ifata umwanya muto mu kazi hamwe n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zisabwa ku kazi kose zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi mu buryo bwimbitse, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kwirinda guhumeka, harimo no gupfuka umunwa n'umutsi iyo ukorora cyangwa witsamura, gutanga udusaku n'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho, kwitegura gukora kure cyangwa gukora amasaha y'akazi igihe bibaye ngombwa, kubuza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi no gukomeza isuku isanzwe n'isukura ry'ibidukikije.
Gushakisha no gutandukanya vuba abantu bashobora kwandura ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abasura n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gitanga inama ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bazaba bamaze nibura amasaha 24 badafite umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro cyangwa indi ndwara, nta miti yo gukiza umuriro cyangwa indi miti ifasha mu kurwanya ibimenyetso. Nanone batanga inama yo gushyiraho politiki yo kuruhuka mu gihe cy'uburwayi, kwemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bitabe ku muntu wo mu muryango urwaye, no kumenyesha abakozi ayo mategeko.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, imirimo ifite ibyago byo kwandura by'umurengera ikubiyemo imirimo isaba ko umuntu ahura kenshi cyangwa hafi cyane, mu ntera ya metero imwe n'igice (6 feet) n'abantu badafite COVID-19 bakekwaho cyangwa bazwiho, ariko bashobora kuba banduye SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'uko abantu bakwirakwiza virusi itera SIDA mu gace k'ikigo cy'ubucuruzi cyangwa bitewe n'uko umuntu aherutse gukora urugendo mpuzamahanga mu karere karimo ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
