Iyo habonetse imikoranire ya hafi mu gihe cyo gufatwa, abakozi bagomba gusukura no gusukura ibikoresho byabo n'imyenda y'akazi mbere yo kongera kubikoresha bakoresheje umufuka cyangwa umuti wo gusukura, kandi bagakurikiza gahunda zisanzwe zo gufunga no kujugunya PPE zikoreshwa, hamwe no gufunga no kumesa imyenda.
