Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abarwayi binjira mu byumba by'abarwayi batandukanywa bitewe n'uko bakekwaho COVID-19. Uretse izindi PPE, OSHA yasabye ko abantu bakora mu birometero 6 by'abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bazwiho SARS-CoV-2 bakoresha udupfukamunwa n'utundi dukoresho dutanga umwuka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, udupfukamunwa two guhumeka N95 twemewe na NIOSH cyangwa se hejuru tugomba gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'ingamba zo kurinda umwuka, harimo no kubigiramo uruhare, amahugurwa n'ibizamini by'abaganga.
Ubundi bwoko bw'udupfukamunwa dushobora kurinda umukozi cyane kandi bikamworohera. OMS ntishyigikira ko umuntu yambara udupfukamunwa kuko COVID-19 ari indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero aho kuba yandurira mu mazi.
OMS isaba ko abakozi bakora ibizamini ku kiraro ari bo bonyine bambara agapfukamunwa.
Ku bantu batora ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, bita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa bakabatwara mu gihe nta buryo bwo gukora aerosol bukorwa, OMS irasaba ko umuntu yambara agapfukamunwa, indorerwamo cyangwa agapfukamunwa, ikanzu n'amaboko.
Iyo habaye uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, agapfukamunwa ka kiruhuko gashyirwa mu mwanya w'agapfukamunwa ka N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko isoko ry'ibiyobyabwenge ridahagije ku isi, OMS isaba ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ikenewe cy'ibiyobyabwenge hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo kuvura abantu hakoreshejwe telefoni, hashyirwaho inzitizi z'umubiri nk'amadirishya asobanutse, abantu bakenera kwitabwaho gusa bakemererwa kugera mu cyumba umurwayi wa COVID-19 aba arimo, hakoreshwa ibiyobyabwenge bikoreshwa mu gikorwa runaka gusa, hakoreshwa agapfukamunwa kamwe mu gihe ari ku barwayi benshi bafite indwara imwe, hakagenzurwa kandi hagakorerwamo ubufatanye mu gucunga ibiyobyabwenge, kandi hakirindwa gukoresha udupfukamunwa ku bantu badafite ibimenyetso.
