Imimerere y'ibiro, uko byerekanwa n'uko byatunganyijwe
Mu cyumweru gishize, twumvise ko umwe mu bo dukorana i San Francisco ashobora kuba yaranduye COVID-19.
Ariko kubera ko twari dufite amakenga, twasabye itsinda ry'abakora isuku yo kwirinda virusi kugira ngo basukure ahantu hose mu biro by'i San Francisco.
Bakoresheje umuti wa virusi wo mu bitaro kugira ngo basukure uturemangingo twose, ndetse n'inzu y'imbere n'ibyumba by'amabati by'abazamukaga binjira mu igorofa ryacu.
Inyubako ikoresha gahunda yayo yo gukora imirimo y'ubwitonzi ikoresha ibicuruzwa byemeza umutekano w'abacyirimo.
Twizeye ko ibiro bizategurwa neza igihe tuzaba tugiye kugaruka.
Ibiro byacu i Washington DC biri mu nzu ya WeWork, yatugejejeho gahunda yayo ya COVID-19 hamwe n'abakozi bose bakorera i Washington DC.
Kuva mu cyumweru gishize, ibiro byacu biri i Washington DC byatangiye gukora mu buryo bwa kure buhuje n'inama zatanzwe n'i San Francisco.
Nk'uko bamwe mu bo dukorana muri New York bazi, twaganiriye no ku cyerekezo cyo gukodesha inzu i Brooklyn.
Ibi biganiro birakomeje ariko bishobora gusubikwa.
Bamwe mu bo dukorana bakora kure ku nshuro ya mbere.
Abo dukorana bamenyereye gukora kure bazi ko guhuza bishobora kugorana kandi bifuza kubaha inama:
Kugabanya igihe cy'amateraniro, ukayashyira mu byiciro by'isaha imwe cyangwa ebyiri gusa.
Niba ari ngombwa ko mwiga igihe kirekire, tekereza ku buryo wakwiga mu minsi myinshi.
Sobanura neza inama, ugire gahunda y'ibyavuzwe, kandi wohereze inyandiko mbere y'igihe.
Gukora amashusho nk'ibisanzwe, hifashishijwe ibikoresho nka Google Docs na Zoom mu rwego rwo gushishikariza ubufatanye n'ibiganiro bihuza abantu.
Kugira umuhuzabikorwa ushinzwe kuyobora buri nama, umuntu ushinzwe kugenzura ikiganiro gihita n'urutonde rw'abavuga, n'umuntu ufasha gufata inyandiko (cyangwa gufata inyandiko rusange).
Kohereza ubutumwa bugufi kuri telefoni y'ubufasha bw'ikoranabuhanga niba ukeneye icyuma gikora neza.
