Itsinda ry'ibikorwa bya HR ririmo kwiga amabwiriza ya ergonomie ashingiye kuri webinari yo gushyigikira kongera imikorere mu kigo.
Mu cyumweru gishize, twasabye abantu bose bahabwa inkunga y'umuryango guhagarika ibikorwa rusange bishyigikirwa na Wikimedia, nk'ibya edit-a-thons, kugeza igihe OMS itangarije ko icyorezo kirangiye.
Twabasobanuriye ko dusobanukiwe ko gusaba guhagarika no guhagarika ibindi bikorwa bishobora gutuma ibikorwa byabo byo gutanga inkunga bitashoboka, kandi ko nta muntu n'umwe uzabazwa igihe ibyo bikorwa bizaba byatinze cyangwa byarahindutse.
Mu cyumweru gitaha, tuzatanga amabwiriza y'inyongera kuri Wikimania n'izindi nama z'abaturage n'iz'akarere.
Imyumvire rusange y'umuryango mpuzamahanga isa n'aho ari agahinda kubera guhungabana no kuruhuka kubera gusobanukirwa no kubona uburyo bwo kwibanda ku miryango yabo, Wikimedia n'ibindi.
Ku bijyanye n'ibikurikira, CRT iri gukora ku kurema page kuri Meta-Wiki kugira ngo itange umwanya kugira ngo umuryango ushobore gukurikirana ingaruka kandi dukomeze itumanaho ryacu na bo.
