LACE2 ni poroteyine ifite uruhu rumwe yo mu bwoko bwa I, ifite ahantu hakorera ingirabuzimafatizo ku maso y'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu bihaha n'izindi.
Urubuga rw'ibinyabuzima rw'ACE2 ruterwa n'urundi rugingo rw'umura rwitwa sheddase; poroteyine iboneka mu maraso irarekurwa, hanyuma ikavanwa mu cyondo.
LACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: lACE2 ifatanye n'uruhu rw'ingirabuzimafatizo cyane cyane mu bice by'ibihaha by'ubwoko bwa II, intaro z'uruhu ruto, intanga z'amaraso n'iz'amaraso, n'intanga z'amaraso z'imitsi y'umubiri mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
