ACE ihindura angiotensin I mu buryo bw'uko angiotensin II ari yo ituma umuntu aba mu mubiri.
LACE2 nayo isohora amino acide ya phenylamine ifite iherezo rya carboxyl ya angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) na hydrolysis mu angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
