Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za telefoni zigamije koroshya gukurikirana abantu mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20, ni ukuvuga kumenya abantu ( abo waganiriye) bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye.
Ibikorwa bitandukanye byatangiye gukorwa cyangwa byatangijwe, hamwe n'ubufasha bwemewe na leta mu turere tumwe na tumwe no mu nzego z'ubutegetsi.
Ibikorwaremezo byinshi byateguwe kugirango hashyirweho porogaramu zo gukurikirana imibonano.
Izo gahunda, cyane cyane izishingira ku kumenya aho abakoresha porogaramu baba, zateza ibibazo by'ibanga.
Hari n'ubundi buryo budahutaza cyane, harimo gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth mu gufata amakuru y'aho umuntu ari n'andi matelefone ngendanwa.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byombi byatangaje ko byashyize mu mikoreshereze ya Android na iOS uburyo bwo gushyigikira izi porogaramu za Bluetooth.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, yatangije porogaramu mu Bushinwa ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba barahuye n'abantu bafite COVID-19.
Ubu ikoreshwa mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa, naho muri Singapuru hakoreshejwe porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Byatewe n'itsinda ry'abashakashatsi mu by'ikoranabuhanga, byatanzwe ku isoko ifunguye kandi bizashyikirizwa leta. Macédoine y'Amajyaruguru yatangije StopKorona! ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth rigamije gukurikirana abantu bashobora kuba baranduye no kuvugana byihuse n'inzego z'ubuzima.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itangazamakuru n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kuva ku ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yavuze ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu iri mu cyiciro cy'iterambere kandi ishobora gutangira mu byumweru biri imbere. Porogaramu nk'iyi iteganyijwe muri Ireland no mu Bufaransa ( StopCovid ).
Australia na Nouvelle Zelande biteganya gushyiraho porogaramu zimeze nka TraceTogether muri Singapuru zishingiye kuri BlueTrace. Uburusiya burashaka gushyiraho porogaramu yo gushakisha ahantu ku barwayi ba COVID-19 baba i Moscou, kugira ngo barebe ko batakwivana mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri kaminuza ya Cambridge wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano, yavuze ku bibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu gukoresha sisitemu zishingiye kuri porogaramu, harimo ibinyoma n'ubushobozi buke bw'imikorere niba igice gito gusa cy'abaturage gikoresha porogaramu.
Mu gusubiza impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry'imikorere y'ibinyoma cyangwa y'uburozi ya coronavirus, Apple yemereye gusa inzego zemewe cyangwa ziringirwa muri rusange kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus kuri App Store.
Google na Amazon byashyizeho ingamba nk'izo.
Abashyigikiye ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka za porogaramu za coronavirus kugenzura abantu benshi, cyane cyane ku isenywa ry'ibikorwa remezo by'ubugenzuzi byashyizweho mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus nyuma y'uko icyago kivuyeho.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura bukorwa ku ngufu bugabanywa.
