Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, ntibari bazi niba ubwandu bwa mbere butanga ubwirinzi bw'igihe kirekire mu bantu bakize.
Uduce tw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri tufatwa nk'aho dushobora kuboneka, dushingiye ku myitwarire y'izindi koronavirusi, ariko hari amakuru y'abantu bakize COVID-19 nyuma yo gupimwa bakagaragaza ko bafite koronavirusi.
Ibi bibazo bifatwa nk'ikigeragezo cy'ubwandu bucyemutse aho kuba kongera kwandura.
Bitekerezwa ko virusi ari kamere kandi ko yakomotse ku nyamaswa, binyuze mu gukwirakwiza ubwandu.
Aho iyi virusi ikomoka ntiharamenyekana, ariko mu Ukuboza 2019 ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara ryari rigizwe gusa n'uko umuntu yandurira undi muntu.
Ubushakashatsi ku bantu 41 ba mbere bagaragaye banduye COVID-19 bwasohotse muri Mutarama 2020 mu kinyamakuru The Lancet bwagaragaje ko itariki ya mbere ibimenyetso byatangiriyeho ari tariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019.
Ibitabo byemewe na OMS byatangaje ko ibimenyetso byatangiye kugaragara ku itariki ya 8 Ukuboza 2019.
Hari ibipimo byinshi bikoreshwa mu gupima urupfu.
Iyi mibare itandukanye bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi ifashwe n'umubare w'ibipimo, ireme ry'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kuvura, igihe cyashize icyorezo gitangiye, hamwe n'ibiranga abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima.
Mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019, OMS yashyizeho kode z'ubutabazi z'ibiza CIM-10 U07.1 ku bantu bapfuye byemejwe mu malaboratoire bishwe na SARS-CoV-2 na U07.2 ku bantu bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19 basuzumwe mu buryo bwa muganga cyangwa mu rwego rw'indwara z'ibyorezo badafite SARS-CoV-2 yemejwe mu malaborative. Umubare w'abapfuye ugereranyije n'uw'abanduye ugaragaza umubare w'abapfuye bagabanyijwemo umubare w'abanduye mu gihe runaka.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ibaruramari rya kaminuza ya Johns-Hopkins, umubare w'abapfuye ku isi ni 6,9% (153 822/2 240 191) kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Mata 2020.
Iyi mibare itandukanye bitewe n'akarere. Ibindi bipimo birimo igipimo cy'ubwandu (CFR) kigaragaza umubare w'abantu basanganywe indwara bapfa bazize iyo ndwara, n'igiciro cy'ubwandu bwandura (IRF) kigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye (bafite cyangwa badafite) bapfa bazize iyo ndwara.
Izi mibare ntabwo zifite igihe gihagije kandi zikurikirana abaturage runaka bafite ubwandu ku iherezo ry'indwara.
Nubwo atari abantu bose banduye bagira udukoko tw'umubiri, kuba dufite udukoko tw'umubiri bishobora kugaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye.
Mu mujyi wa Castiglione d'Adda mu Butaliyani, umujyi muto utuwe n'abaturage 4600, 80 muri bo (1,7%) bamaze gupfa.
Muri Gangelt, iyi ndwara yakwirakwiriye mu minsi mikuru, no mu rubyiruko, bituma umubare w'abapfa uba muto, kandi abantu bose bapfuye bazira COVID-19 bashobora kuba batigeze bashyirwa mu byiciro by'abapfuye.
Byongeye kandi, uburyo bw'ubuvuzi bw'u Budage ntibwaguye mu nkokora.
Mu Buholandi, abantu bagera kuri 3% bashobora kuba bafite udupfukamunwa, nk'uko bigaragazwa n'igenzura ry'abatanga amaraso.
Abantu 69 bapfuye (0,004% by'abaturage) byemejwe ko bafitanye isano na COVID-19.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo n'umubare w'abapfa bitandukanye mu bagabo no mu bagore.
Urupfu ni runini mu bantu mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani.
Ibyago byo kurwara indwara z'ibihaha ni byinshi ku bagabo bafite imyaka 50, kuko itandukaniro hagati y'abagabo n'abagore ryiyongeraho imyaka 90 gusa.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa wari 2.8% mu bagabo na 1.7% mu bagore.
Impamvu nyayo zituma habaho itandukaniro hagati y'abagabo n'abagore ntiziramenyekana, ariko hari aho bishobora kuba biterwa n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima hamwe n'imyifatire.
Itandukaniro ry'imiti y'igitsina gore, kugabanuka kw'umubare w'abagore banywa itabi, no kuba abagabo barwara indwara z'amaraso nk'umuvuduko w'amaraso mu gihe cy'imyaka mike ugereranyije n'abagore, bishobora kuba byaratumye abagabo bapfa cyane.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye bari abagabo, naho 72% by'abishwe na COVID-19 bari abagabo.
Muri Mata 2020, leta ya Amerika ntiyakusanya amakuru ajyanye n'ubwoko bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara ziterwa na virusi nka Ebola, SIDA, ibicurane na SARS, ziterwa n'abagabo n'abagore mu buryo butandukanye.
Umubare munini w'abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, ni abagore kandi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura virusi.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) watangaje ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020 ko izina ry'iki cyorezo ari  COVID-19 .
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus yasobanuye ko CO isobanura corona, VI isobanura virus na D isobanura indwara, 19 ikaba ari yo ya mbere yamenyekanye ko yateye: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Izina ryatoranyijwe kugira ngo hatagira havugwa ahantu runaka (urugero: Ubushinwa), ubwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, hakurikijwe amabwiriza mpuzamahanga yo gushyiraho amazina agamije kwirinda gutesha agaciro. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa coronavirus 2 ifitanye isano n'indwara ifata imyakura (SARS-CoV-2).
OMS ikoresha kandi virusi ya COVID-19 n'iyi virusi mu itangazamakuru ryayo.
Indwara na virusi byombi byitwa  coronavirus .
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabereye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byahoze byitwa coronavirus na Wuhan coronavirus.
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yasabye ko hazajya hakoreshwa amazina y'indwara y'agateganyo 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze kuri virusi n'indwara, hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo mu 2015 yo kwirinda gukoresha ahantu mu mazina y'indwara na virusi.
Amazina yemewe ya COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yasohotse ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Bitewe n'ubushobozi buciriritse bw'imitangire y'ibikoresho, hari abahanga mu gukora ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki basohora ibikoresho byo kwita ku barwayi nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka n'ibikoresho byo guhumeka.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byasabaga valve y'ubuhumekero mu buryo bwihutirwa, kandi umuturage atabashije kuyigura mu gihe gikwiriye, uruganda rwo muri ako gace rwatangije gukora igishushanyo mbonera no gucapa valve 100 zisabwa mu ijoro rimwe.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19, ibitekerezo by'ubugambanyi, amakuru y'ibinyoma n'ibinyoma byatangiye kuvugwa ku nkomoko, ubukana, kwirinda, kuvura n'ibindi byerekeye iyi ndwara, kandi byarakwirakwiriye kuri interineti mu buryo bwihuse.
Bisa n'aho abantu bashobora gukwirakwiza indwara ku zindi nyamaswa zimwe na zimwe.
Ubushakashatsi ntibwigeze bubona ibimenyetso byerekana ko virusi yihindura mu ngurube, mu du na mu nkoko.
Nta muti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe kuvura iyi ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku rukingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 ubu burakorwa n'imiryango ya leta, amatsinda y'abanyeshuri n'abashakashatsi mu nganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije igerageza rya SOLIDARITY ryo gusuzuma ingaruka zo kuvura za virusi enye zisanzwe ziteye icyizere cyane.
Nta rukingo ruboneka, ariko inzego nyinshi zirimo gukora mu buryo bw'ingirakamaro inkingo z'abakandida.
Ibikorwa bya mbere kuri SARS-CoV bikoreshwa kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha uburyo bwo kwakira lACE 2 mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuntu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira burimo gushakishwa.
Icya mbere, abashakashatsi barimo bagerageza gukora urukingo rwa virusi yose.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyi, yaba idafite ingufu cyangwa yapfuye, bigamije gutuma umubiri w'umuntu ugira imbaraga zo kwirinda indwara vuba mu gihe umuntu yongeye kwandura COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, inkingo zishingiye ku byiciro by'ingenzi, zigamije gukora urukingo rutuma abadepite b'umubiri bagira ubushake bwo kurwanya ibice by'ingenzi by'iyo virusi.
Ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, ubushakashatsi bwibanda kuri poroteyine S ifite umugozi w'uruziga ifasha virusi kwinjira mu cyiciro cya ACE 2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni inkingo z'ibinyabutabire (inkingo za ADN cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo guhanga inkingo).
Inkingo zigerageza zaturutse muri izo ngamba zose zigomba kugeragezwa ku birebana n'umutekano n'ibyazo. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, ikigeragezo cya mbere cy'urukingo cyatangiye ku bantu bane bitangiye gukora mu mujyi wa Seattle.
Urukingo rurimo kode ya jenoside itagira icyo itwaye ikururwa kuri virusi iteza indwara. Gukora ku buryo budafite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 byavuzwe ko bishobora kuba imbogamizi mu gukora urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, ariko biravuguruzwa.
Muri Mata 2020, ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 birimo gukorwa.
Ibizamini birindwi byasuzumye imiti yemewe yo kurwanya malariya, harimo n'icyigisho cy'ibanze cy'ibikomoka kuri hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Imiti ya virusi ihindurwa imiterere ni yo igize ubushakashatsi bwinshi mu Bushinwa, hamwe n'ibizamini by'ubushakashatsi by'icyiciro cya gatatu cy'imiti icyenda ya remdesivir mu bihugu byinshi biteganyijwe ko bizatangazwa mu mpera za Mata.
Igenzura ry'iterambere ry'imiti n'inkingo bya COVID-19 byari byatangiye muri Mata 2020. Imiti myinshi irimo kurwanya virusi iri kugeragezwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir, kloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir na lopinavir/ritonavir ifatanyije na interferon beta.
Amakuru y'agateganyo agaragaza ko umuti wa remdesivir wari ufite akamaro muri Werurwe 2020.
Habonetse ubwiyongere mu buvuzi mu barwayi bavurwa na remdesivir mu gihe ikoreshwa mu buryo bw'impuhwe.
Ibizamini by'ibanze by'icyiciro cya III birimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Chloroquine, yari yarigeze gukoreshwa mu kuvura malariya, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, hagaragazwa ibisubizo bya mbere.
Icyakora, hari bamwe basaba ko ubushakashatsi bukorwa ku giti cyabo.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima mu Bushinwa no muri Koreya bashishikariza ikoreshwa rya chloroquine.
Ariko ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe Virology, nubwo cyatangaza ko umuntu agomba gufata ingero ya gram imwe ku munsi, kivuga ko kwikuba kabiri ari akaga cyane kandi bishobora no kumuhitana.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yemereye ikoreshwa rya hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine hakurikijwe uburenganzira bw'ikoreshwa ry'ubutabazi mu buryo bwihutirwa ku buryo bushoboka ku baganga bavura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko hakenewe ingano nyinshi za ribavirin mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.
Nitashyoxanide yagiriwe inama yo gukomeza kwiga in vivo nyuma yo kugaragaza inhibition yo ku gipimo cyo hasi cya SARS-CoV-2. Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko poroteyine ya spicule yambere itangira ikoreshwa na serine 2 transmembrane protease (TMPRSS2) ari ingenzi mu kwinjira kwa SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhuza na lACE 2.
Ubushakashatsi ku miti ya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa idafite, bufite imbogamizi zikomeye zatumye umuryango w'ubuvuzi udashobora kwemera iyi miti nta bushakashatsi bw'inyongera. Loseltamivir ntabwo ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 in vitro kandi nta ruhare ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Igituntu cy'imiti gishobora kuba imbogamizi mu byiciro by'inyuma bya COVID-19 ikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko Lhydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya cytocin. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'Ubushinwa nyuma y'uko hakorewe ubushakashatsi buto.
Hari igerageza ry'icyiciro cya 2 ritemewe mu rwego rw'igihugu mu Butaliyani nyuma yo kugaragaza ibisubizo byiza mu bantu bafite indwara ikomeye.
Iyo ikoreshwa ifatanyije n'ibipimo by'amaraso bya ferritin mu maraso kugira ngo hamenyekane igitera cyotoxin, igomba kurwanya ibintu bikekwa ko ari byo byateje urupfu mu bantu bamwe na bamwe.
Interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yemejwe na FDA ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bw'imimerere bwakozwe nyuma mu kuvura indwara yo guhanagura sitokine zidakunda gukoresha steroid ziterwa n'ikindi cyorezo, ari cyo CAR T cells, mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu nta bimenyetso byakozwe ku ngufu kandi byunganijwe bigaragaza ko tocilizumab ari umuti w'ingirakamaro wo kuvura SCR.
Kwimura udukoko tw'umubiri tw'abantu bakira COVID-19 ku bantu babikeneye, birimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'uburyo butari urukingo bwo kuboneza urubyaro.
Ubu buryo bwashyizwe mu igeragezwa rya SARS ariko nta ngaruka zifatika bwagize.
Kugabanya virusi ni uburyo bwo gukora busaba ko imiti igwanya SARS-CoV-2 yakwirindwa.
Icyakora, ibindi byiciro by'imikorere nka cytotoxicity y'ingirabuzimafatizo n'ibinyabuzima by'ingirabuzimafatizo na/cyangwa phagocytosis bishobora kubaho.
Ibindi byiciro by'ubuvuzi bwa antibiyotike butarangwa n'ubushake, urugero nko gukoresha udukoko tw'umubiri umwe tw'igihimba cy'umubiri, birimo gukorwa.
Umusaruro wa serum y'abarwayi bakize, igizwe n'igice cy'umunyu w'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize, gifite udukoko tw'ubwirinzi bwihariye kuri iyi virusi, ushobora kwiyongera kugira ngo ikwirakwizwe vuba.
